title: Sahara
text: Ai Sahara es big <a href="desert">desert</a> i' <a href="Afreka">Afreka</a>. Ai nam "sahara" i' <a href="Erabek">Erabek</a> wod f' "desert". Orn d' north idda <a href="Medittaraniyan%20See">Medittaraniyan See</a>, to d' west idda <a href="Etlantic%20Oshen">Etlantic Oshen</a>, an to d' east idda <a href="Red%20See">Red See</a>.
linked_text: Ai Sahara es big desert i' [[Afreka]]. Ai nam "sahara" i' [[Erabek]] wod f' "desert". Orn d' north idda Medittaraniyan See, to d' west idda [[Etlantic Oshen]], an to d' east idda Red See.

title: Norfuk Ailen
text:
Norfuk Ailen esa <a href="ailen">ailen</a> i' t' <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a>. Ofisholi a' Teritrii a' Norfuk Ailen, es ner <a href="Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a>, <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a> an <a href="Nyuu%20Kaledonya">Nyuu Kaledonya</a>, a' es 34 km2 airea. A' ailen es iist o' <a href="Ewan%27s%20He-ed">Ewan's He-ed</a> in Ostrielya. Teda, mani a' dem Norfuk Ailenas descend f' dem myuutinias o' HMS Baunti. Dis es b'cause dem Pitkernas setl'd t' ailen wen <a href="Pitkern%20Ailen">Pitkern Ailen</a> b'kam tuu smaal f' t' enkriisin' popyulayshun.
Jiiografii.
Norfuk Ailen es i' t' <a href="Tasman%20Sii">Tasman Sii</a>, paat a' sowth <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a>. A' ailen es iist o' <a href="Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a> en north o' <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a>.
Dems n' <a href="laik">laik</a> a' <a href="riveh">riveh</a> o' Norfuk, a' 32 km o' koestliin. A' koestliin es mainlii em klif a' presipis. <a href="Maun%20Biets">Maun Biets</a> (319m) es t' haies point a' t' ailen, an es neya <a href="Maun%20Pitt">Maun Pitt</a> (318m). Norfuk Ailen teritrii enkluud tu letl ailens; <a href="Felep%20ailen">Felep ailen</a> en <a href="Nepeyan%20ailen">Nepeyan ailen</a>.
<a href="Kingston">Kingston</a> es t' ofishol kapitel, but <a href="Ban%20Pain">Ban Pain</a> es t' mien toen an "de facto" kapitel a' t' Ailen.
Histrei.
Norfuk Ailen setl'd iyas en iyas agoe b' dem salan from Nyuu Ziilan abaut 1300–1400 CE. Dem salan laas sam jenereshien on a' ailen.
T' fas Urupean to lan orn a' ailen was Kaptaan <a href="James%20Cook">James Cook</a> in 1774. Hii giiw a' niem Norf'k Ailen, afta a <a href="Dachess%20a%27%20Norf%27k">Dachess a' Norf'k</a>.
Afta a' <a href="Fas%20Fliit">Fas Fliit</a> setl'd a' <a href="Port%20Jakson">Port Jakson</a>, Lieutenant <a href="Philip%20Gidley%20King">Philip Gidley King</a> got to Norfuk on t' <a href="6th%20o%27%20Maach">6th o' Maach</a>, <a href="1788">1788</a>. Dis konwikt setlment laas entil 1814. A' fas setlment s' cos a' <a href="Royal%20Naewi">Royal Naewi</a> want a' <a href="moo-oo">moo-oo</a> from t' ailen. A setlment duu laas lorng, cos a' moo-oo no gude f' shep.
A' sekan konwikt setlment laas from 1825 t' 1855 iyas. Dieh setlment s' <a href="piinl%20setlment">piinl setlment</a> en em kondishans orn a ailen kaaduu. Em <a href="komandant">komandant</a> s' behd. A' sekan setlment s' end en 1855 cos a' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yuunaited Kingd'm</a> s' end <a href="transportieshan">transportieshan</a>.
Norfuk Ailen s' setld bai em <a href="Pitkern%20Ailen">Pitkernas</a> o' <a href="Juun%206">Juun 6</a>, <a href="1856">1856</a>. Dem Pitkernas s' desend from a' <a href="myuutenias">myuutenias</a> o' <a href="HMS%20Baunti">HMS Baunti</a>. I' <a href="1914">1914</a> iya, a' ailen se enkluud i' <a href="Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a> esa <a href="ekstirnal%20teritrii%20%28Ostrielya%29">ekstirnal teritrii</a>.

title: Pitkern Ailen
text:
Ai Pitkern Ailen esa <a href="ailen">ailen</a> i t' <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a>. Es part a' Yunitid Kingdum teritrii. Pitkern Ailen setl'd iyas en iyas agoe b' dem salan f' Baunti on Jaenyuweri 15 in 1790 wi' soom salan Tahityan. Dem Pitkerna s' desend f' a' myuutenias o' HMS Baunti. T' ailen se include i' Yunitid Kingdum esa ekstirnal teritrii. Esa ailen f' dem Pitkern Ailen.
<a href="Adamstoen">Adamstoen</a> es ofishol kapitel an uni toen an citii o' t' ailen.
Kulchur.
Langgwidc.
T' ofishol langgwidc f' ai Pitkern Ailen es Pitkern. Pitkern (tuu Norfuk) es a' langgwidc daa es spokn i' Norfuk ailen tuu. Es a' miks a' oel Inglish en Tahityan langgwidc, wi' Inglish maeken mor enfluens.
Rilijin.
T' uni kirk a' t' ailen esa kongregayshun o' t' Sewent Day Adventist Kirk. T' kirk esn't a' stait rilijin for no lous rigarding et's establishment hauf biin passed. Et waa a' Adventist misyun i' dem 1890s daa waa instrumental a' konwerting dem Pitkerna t' Sewent Day Adventism. I' dem riisent iyas, t' atendens a' t' kirk haa deklin'd. A' 2000, eight a' dem fortii Pitkerna a' t' tiem atend'd serwises a' t' kirk regyularlii. A' spaait a' daa, most did atend a' speshul okasyuns.
T' kirk waa bilt i' 1954. Es manaj'd b' t' residint pastor an t' board a' t' kirk. T' pastor serfs a' tuu-iya term.

title: Biiolojii
text:
Biiolojii esa <a href="saiens">saiens</a>, daa studehs laaef, dem plaant an dem anamal. Dem sub-disiplins a' biiolojii ar diifin'd b' dem riiserch siistems employ'd an t' typ a' siistem studii'd: tiioretikel biiolojii yuuses matematikel siistems t' formyulayt dem kwantitaytiw models whil eksperitmentil biilojii performs empirikel eksperiments t' tes t' waliditii a' propos'd teriis an understan dem mekanisms underliiin lyf an hou et look'd an iiwolw'd f' nor-liwin matta abaut 4 billiion yias agoe truu a gradjual enkriis i' t' kompleksitii a' t' siistem. Sii dem branches a' biiolojii f' mor. Dem salan s' study biiolojii a' koel biiolojist. Biiolojii w' faas difiin a' saiens i' t' <a href="19th%20cenchurii">19th cenchurii</a>.

title: Erabek
text:
Erabek es em <a href="Erab">Erab</a> <a href="laenghwij">laenghwij</a>. Et es simis t' <a href="Hiibruu">Hiibruu</a> an <a href="Auramaik">Auramaik</a>. Erabek es spoken all ower t' woerld, but most i' t' <a href="Medl%20Eist">Medl Eist</a>. 
'Bout 250 milyan salan speaken Erabek, en t' <a href="laenghwij">laenghwij</a> i' weri emportent t' dem <a href="muslim">muslim</a>, a' dem <a href="muslim">muslim</a> biliwe a' <a href="God">God</a> yuus a' t' tark t' <a href="Mohamid">Mohamid</a>, a' giiwe hii t' <a href="Koran">Koran</a>.
Mani word i' <a href="Norfuk">Norfuk</a> a' <a href="Pitkern">Pitkern</a> a' f' Erabek, liik "shuga" a' "koton".

Mani word i' [[Norfuk]] a' [[Pitkern]] a' f' Erabek, liik "shuga" a' "koton".

title: Pitkern Anthem
text:
T' Pitkern Anthem es wun <a href="nashunal%20anthem">nashunal anthem</a> o' <a href="Norfuk%20Ailen">Norfuk Ailen</a> an <a href="Pitkern%20Ailen">Pitkern Ailen</a>. I' es neiimed Come Ye Blessed en Inglish.
Liriiks (Inglish).
Then shall the KingSay unto themOn his right hand:Come ye blessed of my FatherInherit the kingdom prepared for youFrom the foundation of the worldI was hungerd and ye gave me meat,I was thirsty and ye gave me drinkI was a stranger and ye took me in,Naked and ye clothed me,I was sick and ye visited me,I was in prison and ye came unto meIn as much ye have done it unto one of the least ofThese my brethrenYe have done it unto me,Ye have done it unto me.
Liriiks (Norfuk/Pitkern).
<poem>
Then gwen daa King
Tal unto dem
Orn hes rait haan:
Kam ye blessed o mais Faada
Inherit daa kingdum prepared f' yuu
Fram daa foundayshun o t' werl
I wos hungaa'd en ye giw mii miit,
I wos thirstii en ye giw mii a drink
I wos a strienja en ye tek mii iin,
Noe klorth en ye klorthd mii,
I wos sor en ye wisitiid mii,
I wos iin pris'n en ye kam unto mii
Iin es mach ye gat dan et unto wan o daa liis o
Thiis mais brethren
Ye gat dan et unto mii,
Ye gat dan et unto mii.
</poem>

title: Adamstoen
text:
Adamstoen esa t' mien toen an a' kapitel citii o' t' <a href="Pitkern%20Ailen">Pitkern Ailen</a>. T' popyulayshun a' 2021 iya es 49 piopel. Esa t' uni settlement a' t' ailen, which esa t' uni inhabited one o' t' teritrii.
Owerwyuu.
T' popyulayshun o' Adamstoen esa t' entire popyulayshun o' t' teritrii o' Pitkern Ailen. Aw o' dem otha ailen i' t' gruup ar uninhabited. Adamstoen esa t' plaes where dem Pitkerna iit, sliip, driink, an elsa esa t' plaes where dem grow fuud i' dem gardens.
Adamstoen esa t' sekan liist popyulas kapitel citii i' t' werl, efta <a href="King%20Edward%20Point">King Edward Point</a> (22 inhabitants) o' <a href="Sowth%20Jorja%20and%20t%27%20Sowth%20Sandwich%20Ailen">Sowth Jorja and t' Sowth Sandwich Ailen</a> (elsa a' teritrii o' t' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdum</a>). Et haa akses t' televisiien an Inteneit, although t' konekyon es much sloer. Et haa telefone elsa but t' mien form o' komyuunikaashun remiens ham radio. 
Adamstoen haa onlii one store daa sells grosheriis an jeneral produkts. Ela there esa post ofis. T' mien striit es kawed t' "Hill o' Difikultii".

title: Inglish
text:
Inglish ("English" /ɪŋglɪʃ/) es a' Jermenik laenghwij.
Inglish ("English") es a' laenghwij tat es spokn a' sefrral kuntriis. Tis laenghwij es cerret n'aal tiis koontriis. Tis laenghwij es taot a'maenii skuulls aal ofr te woerelt. Ets enfluens s'efekting Norfuk vaerii mootc. Inglish es wun aof te moust emportent laenghwijes a'te woerelt. Te histrei f'Inglic es kampliketet. Es aridcineyts a 'Inglen.

title: Ingland
text: Ingland esa t' biges kuntrii i' t' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdum</a>. T' kapitel citii es <a href="London">London</a>. 'Bout 60 million piopel liiw i' Ingland. Kuntrii es neya <a href="Skotlund">Skotlund</a> a' <a href="Waals">Waals</a>. <a href="Inglish%20Channel">Inglish Channel</a> (La Mansh) es siipareitiid Inglaf f' kontenental <a href="France">France</a>.

title: Ostrielya
text: Ostrielya esa kuntrii i' <a href="Osheania">Osheania</a>, a' t' kontenent <a href="Kontenent%20Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a>. Ets west a' <a href="Norfuk%20Ailen">Norfuk Ailen</a> an t' mos a' t' res a' Osheania, sowth a' <a href="Papua%20Nyuu%20Gini">Papua Nyuu Gini</a>, north a' t' <a href="Sowthern%20Oshen">Sowthern Oshen</a> an <a href="Antartica">Antarktika</a>, an iist a' t' <a href="Indien%20Oshen">Indien Oshen</a>.

title: Kurencii
text: Kurencii esa <a href="unit">unit</a> a' <a href="mani">mani</a>. Som a' em kurencii a' <a href="Ostrielyan%20dola">Ostrielyan dola</a>, <a href="Uro">Uro</a>, <a href="Pownd%20sturleng">Pownd sturleng</a>, <a href="Poelish%20slotii">Poelish slotii</a>, <a href="Ejiiptyan%20pownd">Ejiiptyan pownd</a>, <a href="Boliwyan%20kurencii">Boliwyan kurencii</a>, <a href="Keniian%20shileng">Keniian shileng</a>, <a href="Eserbeyjani%20manat">Eserbeyjani manat</a>, <a href="Croayshan%20kuuna">Croayshan kuuna</a>, <a href="Libiian%20denar">Libiian denar</a> an <a href="Solamon%20Ailen%20dola">Solamon Ailen dola</a>. Kurencii ken aslo be siin i' elektoneek forms sutch as' dem <a href="Bitkoin">bitkoines</a> an dem <a href="Kredeiyt%20kaard">kredeiyt kaardz</a>.

text: Hiidrojen esa <a href="kemikil%20element">kemikil element</a>, a' es <a href="nambe">nambe</a> wan a' d' <a href="pieriodik%20taebl">pieriodik taebl</a>. "H" es t' kemikil simbil o' hiidrojen. title: Worsaaw
text:
Worsaaw esa kapitel citii a' <a href="Poeland">Poeland</a>. Tuu milyan salan liw a' Worsaaw, dem salan a' naem "Varsovians".
Histrei.
Dem salan bigan liwen i' t' airea i' t' thertiinth centurii. I' t' fiftiinth centurii, a' bicaiim citii. Es s' bicaiim kapitel o' Poeland i' t'iya <a href="1596">1596</a>. Bitwiin <a href="1939">1939</a> a' <a href="1945">1945</a>, Worsaaw s' okupiid b' <a href="Doichland">Doichland</a>. A' <a href="Jaenyuweri%2017">Jaenyuweri 17</a>, <a href="1945">1945</a>, t' <a href="USSR">USSR</a> s' inta t' citii, en saau a' dem <a href="Nertsii">Nertsii</a> s' distroii t' old citii. Aafta t' waa, <a href="Boleslaw%20Bierut">Boleslaw Bierut</a> rayjiim s' mayk Worsaaw kapitel o' t' <a href="Salan%20Repablik%20o%27%20Poeland">Salan Repablik o' Poeland</a>.
linked_text: Worsaaw esa kapitel citii a' [[Poeland]]. Tuu milyan salan liw a' Worsaaw, dem salan a' naem "Varsovians". Histrei. Dem salan bigan liwen i' t' airea i' t' thertiinth centurii. I' t' fiftiinth centurii, a' bicaiim citii. Es s' bicaiim kapitel o' Poeland i' t'iya 1596. Bitwiin 1939 a' 1945, Worsaaw s' okupiid b' [[Doichland]]. A' [[Jaenyuweri 17]], 1945, t' USSR s' inta t' citii, en saau a' dem Nertsii s' distroii t' old citii. Aafta t' waa, Boleslaw Bierut rayjiim s' mayk Worsaaw kapitel o' t' Salan Repablik o' Poeland.

title: Brisbin
text:
Brisbin esa citii i' <a href="Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a>. Es kapitel o' t' stait a' <a href="Kwiinsland">Kwiinsland</a>. T' popyulayshun s' es 1,810,943 i' <a href="2005">2005</a>. Esa therd biges citii i' Ostrielya, en d' biges i' Kwiinsland.
Histrei.
B'for dem <a href="Urup">Urup</a>ean liiwd defe, t' siit o' Brisbin s' enhabit a' dem <a href="Aborijinal">Aborijinal</a> salan. <a href="Matthyu%20Flindaas">Matthyu Flindaas</a> fas s' eksplor t'airea a' <a href="1797">1797</a>. Lata, a' <a href="Oktoeba%2023">Oktoeba 23</a>, <a href="1823">1823</a>, <a href="Jon%20Okslii">Jon Okslii</a> s' caim o' d'shep "Mermaid", en s' sail t' Kwiinsland. Okslii s' diskova t' <a href="Brisbin%20Riveh">Brisbin Riveh</a>, s' sail uppa modan-dai <a href="Okslii%20Criik">Okslii Criik</a>.
Lata, a' <a href="1824">1824</a>, Leftenant Milla s' istablish kolonii a' <a href="Redklif">Redklif</a>, b'for s' relokat a' t'Brisbin Riveh. A' popyulayshun a' Brisbin a' t'end o' <a href="1825">1825</a> a' "45 mail a' 2 fimail".
En <a href="1859">1859</a>, Kwiinsland s' proklaaim a' difrent colonii f' <a href="Niiw%20Sowth%20Waayls">Niiw Sowth Waayls</a>, a' Brisbin s' choos a' t' kapitel. Lata, a' <a href="1902">1902</a>, Brisbin s' enkorpiraat a' citii.
linked_text: Brisbin esa citii i' [[Ostrielya]]. Es kapitel o' t' stait a' [[Kwiinsland]]. T' popyulayshun s' es 1,810,943 i' 2005. Esa therd biges citii i' Ostrielya, en d' biges i' Kwiinsland. Histrei. B'for dem [[Urup]]ean liiwd defe, t' siit o' Brisbin s' enhabit a' dem Aborijinal salan. [[Matthyu Flindaas]] fas s' eksplor t'airea a' 1797. Lata, a' Oktoeba 23, 1823, Jon Okslii s' caim o' d'shep "Mermaid", en s' sail t' Kwiinsland. Okslii s' diskova t' Brisbin Riveh, s' sail uppa modan-dai Okslii Criik. Lata, a' 1824, Leftenant Milla s' istablish kolonii a' Redklif, b'for s' relokat a' t'Brisbin Riveh. A' popyulayshun a' Brisbin a' t'end o' 1825 a' "45 mail a' 2 fimail". En 1859, Kwiinsland s' proklaaim a' difrent colonii f' Niiw Sowth Waayls, a' Brisbin s' choos a' t' kapitel. Lata, a' 1902, Brisbin s' enkorpiraat a' citii.

title: Daarwin
text:
Daarwin esa citii i' <a href="Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a>. S' t' kapitel o' t' <a href="Northan%20Teritrii">Northan Teritrii</a>. T' popyulayshun s' es 111,300, a' <a href="2005">2005</a> iya.
Histrei.
B'for dem Urupa liiwd defe, t' <a href="Laraikya">Laraikya</a> <a href="Aborijinal">Aborijinal</a> salan liiwd a' t' siit. I' t' <a href="1600s">1600s</a>, t' <a href="Duch">Duch</a> s' wisit Ostrielya north koest, en se miek map o' t' airea. <a href="John%20Stoks">John Stoks</a> o' t' <a href="HMS%20Biigl">HMS Biigl</a> fas salan s' sii Daarwin haaba, i' <a href="1839">1839</a>. Hi s' naam t' haaba aafta <a href="Chaarls%20Daarwin">Chaarls Daarwin</a>, a British nachurelist a' se sail o' t' Biigl b'for.
linked_text: Daarwin esa citii i' [[Ostrielya]]. S' t' kapitel o' t' [[Northan Teritrii]]. T' popyulayshun s' es 111,300, a' 2005 iya. Histrei. B'for dem Urupa liiwd defe, t' Laraikya Aborijinal salan liiwd a' t' siit. I' t' 1600s, t' [[Duch]] s' wisit Ostrielya north koest, en se miek map o' t' airea. title: Northan Teritrii
text:
Northan Teritrii esa fedrel <a href="teritrii">teritrii</a> i' t' north o' <a href="Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a>. <a href="Daarwin">Daarwin</a> esa kapitel a' biges citii, <a href="Alis%20Springs">Alis Springs</a> a' <a href="Ten%27nent%20Criik">Ten'nent Criik</a> a' otha citii.
Jiiografii.
Northan Teritrii esa't sentril-north o' Ostrielya, eist o' <a href="West%20Ostrielya">West Ostrielya</a>, north o' <a href="Sowth%20Ostrielya">Sowth Ostrielya</a>, a' west o' <a href="Kwiinsland">Kwiinsland</a>. Tuu em rok formashun, <a href="Uluru">Eirs Rok</a> (Uluru) a' <a href="Dem%20Olga">Dem Olga</a> a' i' teritrii. <a href="Kakadu%20Nashunul%20Paark">Kakadu Nashunul Paark</a> a'i' north o' t' teritrii.
linked_text: Northan Teritrii esa fedrel teritrii i' t' north o' [[Ostrielya]]. [[Daarwin]] esa kapitel a' biges citii, [[Alis Springs]] a' Ten'nent Criik a' otha citii. Jiiografii. Northan Teritrii esa't sentril-north o' Ostrielya, eist o' West Ostrielya, north o' [[Sowth Ostrielya]], a' west o' [[Kwiinsland]]. Tuu em rok formashun, Eirs Rok (Uluru) a' Dem Olga a' i' teritrii. Kakadu Nashunul Paark a'i' north o' t' teritrii.

title: Jesus
text:
Jesus (also Jesus o' Nasarith), esa biges figur i' <a href="kreschenitii">kreschenitii</a>. Dem kreshen biliwe a' Jesus esa <a href="Mesier">Mesier</a>, a' dem <a href="muslim">muslim</a> biliwe Jesus esa <a href="profet">profet</a>, a' dem jua biliwe Jesus esa profet.
En kreschenitii.
En kreschenitii, t' liife o' Jesus es s' tel i' em <a href="Gospil">Gospil</a>, i' t' <a href="Niiw%20Testimint">Niiw Testimint</a> o' t' <a href="Biibl">Biibl</a>. Dem Gospil was s' riit b' salan t' follow Jesus, dem <a href="aposil">aposil</a>. T' for maain em gospil a' <a href="John%20%28Gospil%29">John</a>, <a href="Mark%20%28Gospil%29">Mark</a>, <a href="Matthew%20%28Gospil%29">Matthew</a> a' <a href="Luke%20%28Gospil%29">Luke</a>.

En kreschenitii. En kreschenitii, t' liife o' Jesus es s' tel i' em Gospil, i' t' Niiw Testimint o' t' Biibl. Dem Gospil was s' riit b' salan t' follow Jesus, dem aposil. T' for maain em gospil a' John, Mark, Matthew a' Luke.

title: Yunitid Staits o' Merika
text: Yunitid Staits, ofisholi Yunitid Staits o' Merika (<a href="Inglish">Inglish</a>: "United States of America") esa <a href="Lyst%20o%27%20kuntrii">kuntrii</a> i' <a href="North%20Merika">North Merika</a>. T' kapitel citii es <a href="Woshingtun%2C%20D.K.">Woshingtun</a>, an t' larges citii es <a href="Nyuu%20York">Nyuu York</a>. T' kuntrii esa <a href="federal%20repablik">federal repablik</a> konsistin o' 50 a' em separaet staits, lorngf' deir ouun government daa shaers suvereinitii lorngf' t' federal government. As well as t' 50 diferent staits, t' federashyuun konsists o' t' <a href="Distrik%20o%27%20Kolumbya">Distrik o' Kolumbya</a> daa esa federal teritri an' dem wariuus poseshens. Wit 3.8 million skwear maels dem Yunitid Staits o' Merika es t' fourth o' em fifth biges kuntriis i' t' Woral. Es s' third mos popyuulus kuntrii o' t' Erth. T' mijoritii o' Merikan teritri es biitwiin <a href="Kaneda">Kaneda</a> an <a href="Meksikoe">Meksikoe</a>.

title: Norfuk
text:
Norfuk (Norf'k) es a kreol <a href="laenghwij">laenghwij</a> spoekn mien orn <a href="Norfuk%20Ailen">Norfuk Ailen</a> an es disendiid fram t' <a href="Pitkern">Pitkern</a> laenghwij a' t' setlas from <a href="Pitkern%20Ailen">Pitkern Ailen</a>. Ets a' miks a' oel <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a> en <a href="Tahityan">Tahityan</a> laenghwij, lorngf' Inglish miekn mor enfluens. Plenti o' em werds iin Norfuk es f' <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a>, laik "<a href="ailen">ailen</a>" ('island') an "<a href="tiemsoen">tiemsoen</a>" ('timezone').
Norfuk es t' ofishol laenghwij, lorngf' Inglish, o' Norfuk Ailen sens 2005. T' orthografii s' dewelap'd bai <a href="Alis%20Baffe">Aelis Baffett</a> an Dr. <a href="Dohnal%20Liekok">Dohnal Liekok</a> es aksepted bai t' Norfuk Ailen gawanment an ets aplekaeshan es enkriisin.
Riilaeshunshep t' Pitkern.
Norfuk es ekposed t' graeta kontakt an enfluens from Inglish dan Pitkern, alla serias komparison a' t' tu laenghwijes haufs nort biin dan.

title: Julius Caesar
text:
Gaius Julius Caesar woos a Roman military and political stiffler. He played a critical role in thur transformation f thur <a href="Roman%20Republic">Roman Republic</a> into thur <a href="Roman%20Empire">Roman Empire</a>.
He woos known for his gri' military victories. His conques' f Gaul extended thur Roman world to thur North Sea, and he also conducted thur firs' Roman invasion f Britain in 55 BC. Caesar took advantage f domestic troubles to fang-howld control f <a href="Rome">Rome</a>. He qoocklie began extensive reforms f Roman society and governmen'. He woos proclaimed Dictator, and heavilie centralised thur booreaucracy f thur Republic. A group f senators, led by Caesar's former friend Marcus Junius Brutus, assassinated thur dictator on thur Ides f March (March 15) in 44 BC, hopin' to restore thur Roman Republic. howsome-ever, thur resul' woos another Roman civil war, which ultimatelie led to thur establishmen' f a permanen' autocracy by Caesar's adopted heir, <a href="Octavian">Octavian</a>.

title: Eswotiini
text:
Eswotiini ulla Swoseland esa kuntrii i' <a href="Afreka">Afreka</a>. Et es border'd b ' <a href="Sowth%20Afreka">Sowth Afreka</a> t' ets north, west an' sowth. Elsa, ets border'd b' Mozambique t' ets northeast. Eswotiini es one o' t' smawest kuntriis a' Afreka.
T' popyulayshun o' Eswotiini es mostlii ethnic Swoses. T' langgwidc o' t' Swoses es siSwati, but Inglish elsa es ofishol. Dem Swoses first establesh'd deir Kingdum in t' 18th centurii under <a href="Ngwane%20III">Ngwane III</a>. T' kuntrii an dem Swoses get deir names f' t' King Mswati II unda whose liidurship Eswotiini teritrii waa yunitid an expand'd; dem present borders waa drawn in 1881. Efta a' konflikt kaw'd t' Sekond Boer War, Eswotiini waa unda t' rule o' t' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdum</a> until independens waa gayn'd a' t' 6 September, 1968. In April 2018 t' name o' t' kuntrii waa chayng'd f' Kingdum o' Swoseland (<a href="Inglish">Inglish</a>: "Kingdom of Swaziland)" t' Kingdum o' Eswotiini (Inglish": Kingdom of Eswatini"). Dis chayng waa t' mirror t' name o' t' kuntrii i' t' siSwati langgwidc. 
T' government o' Eswotiini esa ebsoluut monarkii, wi' t' King <a href="Mswati%20III">Mswati III</a> a' ets present soweran since 1986. Eleksyuuns a' held every five iyas t' determine t' komposisyuun o' t' House o' Esembli an t' Senate. T' current konstitusyuun waa adoptit in 2005. Howeva, biikaus Eswotiini esa ebsoluut monarkii t' word o' t' King es final.
Eswotiini esa developing kuntrii, an haa serious health issues. Ets t' kuntrii w' t' highest rate o' HIV/AIDS i' t' werl. A' o' 2018, Eswotiini haa t' 12th-lowest life ekspektansy i' t' werl, a' 58 iyas.

Howeva, biikaus Eswotiini esa ebsoluut monarkii t' word o' t' King es final. [[Eswotiini]] esa developing kuntrii, an haa serious health issues. Ets t' kuntrii w' t' highest rate o' HIV/AIDS i' t' werl. [[A]]' o' 2018, [[Eswotiini]] haa t' 12th-lowest life ekspektansy i' t' werl, a' 58 iyas.

text:
Kataa (<a href="Erabek">Erabek</a>: قطر [ˈqɑtˁɑr]‎) esa kuntrii (<a href="emiraiit">emiraiit</a>) i' t’ <a href="Medl%20Eist">Medl Eist</a>, i' <a href="Asya">Asya</a>. Et bordas <a href="Saudi%20Erabia">Saudi Erabia</a> a' sowth, an a' west, north an eist deya esa <a href="Persidiaan%20Gyuulf">Persidiaan Gyuulf</a>. "De facto", a' wata, Kataa orlsoe bordas <a href="Barain">Barain</a> an <a href="Yunitid%20Erab%20Emiraiits">Yunitid Erab Emiraiits</a>. T' kapitel an t' biges citii es <a href="Doha">Doha</a>.
Jiografii.
Airea.
Kuwaa a' <a href="airea">airea</a> o' 11 586 km². Neyali orl a' teritrii a' Kataa esa <a href="desert">desert</a>.
Gidrografii.
Deya esa nor <a href="Riveh">rivehs</a> i' Kataa, uni 5–7 big <a href="Wadii">wadiis</a> (<a href="Erabek">Erabek</a>: وَادِي‎): Wadii-Asma, Wadii-Banat, Wadii-Debayaan, Wadii-Ziab, Wadii-Girbaan, Wadii-Huvaiila an Wadii-Lusail. Wadii esa a' Erabek naiim o' wet striimbit o' rivehs.
Histrei.
Siins VII cenchurii Kataa wos a' teritrii o' <a href="Erabek%20Kalifaat">Erabek Kalifaat</a>, dyuurin' XIII — XIV cenchuriis, o' <a href="Barain">Barain</a>, a' t' beginiin o' XVI cenchurii, o' <a href="Porchugal">Porchugal</a>, aafta, o' <a href="Ottoman%20Empaye">Ottoman Empaye</a>. I' 1916 — 1971 iyas, Kataa wos t' protektoraiit o' t' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdum</a>. A' Septemba 3, t' letl kuntrii gaiin'd ets <a href="independens">independens</a>. T' <a href="Nayshunal%20Dieh%20o%27%20Kataa">Nayshunal Dieh o' Kataa</a> esa Desemba 18.

T' kapitel an t' biges citii es Doha. Jiografii. Airea. Kuwaa a' airea o' 11 586 km². Neyali orl a' teritrii a' Kataa esa desert. Gidrografii. Deya esa nor rivehs i' Kataa, uni 5–7 big wadiis ([[Erabek]]: وَادِي‎): Wadii-Asma, Wadii-Banat, Wadii-Debayaan, Wadii-Ziab, Wadii-Girbaan, Wadii-Huvaiila an Wadii-Lusail. Wadii esa a' Erabek naiim o' wet striimbit o' rivehs. Histrei. Siins VII cenchurii Kataa wos a' teritrii o' Erabek Kalifaat, dyuurin' XIII — XIV cenchuriis, o' [[Barain]], a' t' beginiin o' XVI cenchurii, o' [[Porchugal]], aafta, o' Ottoman Empaye. I' 1916 — 1971 iyas, Kataa wos t' protektoraiit o' t' [[Yunitid Kingdum]]. A' Septemba 3, t' letl kuntrii gaiin'd ets [[independens]]. T' Nayshunal Dieh o' Kataa esa Desemba 18.

title: Nauruu
text: T' Repablik a' Nauruu (also spelt Ripublik Naoero) esa ailen kuntrii i' <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a>. Et es part o' Mikronesya. Dem Nauruuans tal an almos nor relatid kaul'd <a href="Nauruuan%20laenghwij">Nauruuan</a>. T' Repablik a' Nauruu es wel known b'cause et es t' mos obiis kuntrii i' t' werld b' persent obiis o owaweiht, wit' a majoritii a' t' kuntriis popyulayshun b'in iida a' dos tuu.

title: North Koriya
text:
, ofisialii Demokratik Piopels Repablik o' Koriya, esa kuntrii i' north-eist Asya, neks t' <a href="Sowth%20Koriya">Sowth Koriya</a>, <a href="Shiina">Shiina</a>, an <a href="Rusha">Rusha</a>. Like their neighbors to t' Sowth, dem North Koriyans klaim aw o' t' Koriyan Peninsula as their ouun teritrii. T' kapitel an laarjist citii es <a href="Pyongyang">Pyongyang</a>.
I' 1910, t' Koriyan Peninsula waa aneksed b' <a href="Japan">Japan</a>, which waa at t' tiem known as t' <a href="Empire%20o%27%20Japan">Empire o' Japan</a>. Afta t' Japanese surrender followin their defeat i' <a href="Werl%20War%20II">Werl War II</a> i' 1945, Koriya waa divided biitwiin t' <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits o' Merika</a> an t' <a href="Sowiet%20Yunyuun">Sowiet Yunyuun</a>. Daa led to t' establishment o' two separate staits from Koriyan teritrii. A' invasion o' t' Sowth bii North Koriya i' 1950 led to t' <a href="Koriyan%20War">Koriyan War</a>. Et ended wi' a' armistice, although no peace treatii waa signed.

title: Isaac Nyuuton
text:
Sir Isaac Nyuuton (4 Jaenyuweri 1643 – 31 Maach 1727) wos a’ Inglish <a href="fisiks">fisisist</a>, <a href="maethamatiks">maethematishen</a>, <a href="estronomii">estronoma</a>, naachurel <a href="filosofii">filosofa</a>, <a href="elkemii">elkemist</a>, en <a href="thiiolojii">thiiolojii</a>an. Hii es thort t’ be wan a’ t’ moes enfluwenshal mien i' histrei bii mani skolas en t’ jenrel pablik as wael.
Hiis buuk, t’ "Philosophiæ Naturalis Principia Mathematic" (elsa koul'd t’ "Principia"), pablish'd in 1687, es bin konsaaideriid wan a’ t’ moes enfluwenshal buuks i' t’ histrei a’ <a href="saiens">saiens</a>.
Hii wos barn i' t' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdum</a>.
linked_text: Sir Isaac Nyuuton (4 Jaenyuweri 1643 – 31 Maach 1727) wos a’ Inglish fisisist, maethematishen, estronoma, naachurel filosofa, elkemist, en [[thiiolojii]]an. Hii es thort t’ be wan a’ t’ moes enfluwenshal mien i' histrei bii mani skolas en t’ jenrel pablik as wael. Hiis buuk, t’ "Philosophiæ Naturalis Principia Mathematic" (elsa koul'd t’ "Principia"), pablish'd in 1687, es bin konsaaideriid wan a’ t’ moes enfluwenshal buuks i' t’ histrei a’ [[saiens]]. Hii wos barn i' t' [[Yunitid Kingdum]].

title: Iista Ailen
text:
Iista Ailen, (Rapa Nui i' t' loekl leanghwij) esa iistern <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a> <a href="ailen">ailen</a>. T' ailen es a' teritrii a' <a href="Chili">Chili</a>. T' ailens kapitel es <a href="Hanga%20Roa">Hanga Roa</a> port. 
Rapa Nui es wan riili aisolaeted ailen, 2075km iist a' <a href="Pitkern%20Ailen">Pitkern Ailen</a> an 415km west a' <a href="Isla%20Salas%20y%20G%C3%B3mez">Isla Salas y Gómez</a> (unenhabited). T' mien ting a' Iista Ailen es dem mo'ai. Dem ar biiliv'd t' b' statchuus a' dem ansestas a' dem Rapa Nui piopel. Dem wer maek'd f' dem materiial a' t' ailen.

title: Wata
text: Wata esa <a href="kemikill%20kompornd">kemikill kompornd</a> wi' t' <a href="kemikill%20formyula">kemikill formyula</a> . A' <a href="Properties%20a%27%20wata">wata molekuul</a> contains wun <a href="oksijen">oksijen</a> an tu <a href="hiidrojen">hiidrojen</a> <a href="etem">etem</a>s konnektiid b' <a href="covalent%20bond">covalent bond</a>s. Wata es a <a href="liquid">liquid</a> a' t' <a href="standid%20ambient%20temperature%20an%20pressure">standid ambient temperature an pressure</a>, but et uulii co-iksists a' t' <a href="Erth">Erth</a> wi' ets <a href="solid">solid</a> staiit, <a href="aes">aes</a>, an <a href="gas">gas</a>eous staiit (<a href="wata%20vapor">wata vapor</a> ulla <a href="stiim">stiim</a>). Wata tuu iksists i' a' <a href="liquid%20crystal">liquid crystal</a> staiit neer <a href="Hydrophile">hydrophilic</a> surfaiisis. Dem anamal niid wata t' servaaew.
linked_text: Wata esa kemikill kompornd wi' t' kemikill formyula . A' wata molekuul contains wun oksijen an tu [[hiidrojen]] [[etem]]s konnektiid b' covalent bonds. title: Spanish
text: T' Spanish laenghwij ("El idioma español") esa Romans laenghwij spoekn i' <a href="Spain">Spain</a>, a' Urupiin kuntrii, an' deir formur empayee i' t' western hemusfiir (<a href="Leten%20Merika">Leten Merika</a>). Esa sekan mos komyuunli spoken laengwij o' <a href="Erth">Erth</a>, an' esa mein laenghwij o' 21 kuntriis, wit 480,000,000 iindiijunus spoekers.. T' laenghwij also haufs a significant amuunt o' spoekers in t' <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits</a>, duu a' t' imugrashun frum Leten Merika a' t' Yunitid Staits. T' kuntrii tuuday haufs mor spoekers o' Spanish dan Spain etself.

title: Norfuk histrei
text:
Norfuk Ailen setl'd iyas en iyas agoe b' dem salan fram Nyuu Ziilan abaut 1300–1400 CE. Dem salan laas sam jenereshien on a' ailen.
T' fas Urupean to lan orn a' ailen was Kaptaan <a href="James%20Cook">James Cook</a> in 1774. Hii giiw a' niem Norf'k Ailen, afta a <a href="Dachess%20a%27%20Norf%27k">Dachess a' Norf'k</a>.
Afta a' <a href="Fas%20Fliit">Fas Fliit</a> setl'd a' <a href="Port%20Jakson">Port Jakson</a>, Lieutenant <a href="Philip%20Gidley%20King">Philip Gidley King</a> got to Norfuk on <a href="Maach%206">Maach 6</a>, <a href="1788">1788</a>. Dis konwikt setlment laas entil 1814. A' fas setlment s' cos a' <a href="Royal%20Naewi">Royal Naewi</a> want a' <a href="moo-oo">moo-oo</a> fram a' ailen. A setlment duu laas lorng, cos a' moo-oo no gude f' shep.
A' sekan konwikt setlment laas fram 1825-1855. Dieh setlment s' <a href="piinl%20setlment">piinl setlment</a> en em kondishans orn a ailen kaaduu. Em <a href="komandant">komandant</a> s' behd. A' sekan setlment s' end en 1855 cos a' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yuunaited Kingd'm</a> s' end <a href="transportieshan">transportieshan</a>.
Norfuk Ailen s' setld bai em <a href="Pitkern%20Ailen">Pitkernas</a> o' <a href="Juun%206">Juun 6</a>, <a href="1856">1856</a>. Dem Pitkernas s' desend fram a' <a href="myuutenias">myuutenias</a> o' <a href="HMS%20Baunti">HMS Baunti</a>. In <a href="1914">1914</a>, a' ailen se enkluud i' <a href="Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a> esa <a href="ekstirnal%20teritrii%20%28Ostrielya%29">ekstirnal teritrii</a>.
linked_text: [[Norfuk Ailen]] setl'd iyas en iyas agoe b' dem salan fram [[Nyuu Ziilan]] abaut 1300–1400 CE. Dem salan laas sam jenereshien on a' ailen. T' fas Urupean to lan orn a' ailen was Kaptaan [[James Cook]] in 1774. Hii giiw a' niem Norf'k Ailen, afta a Dachess a' Norf'k. Afta a' Fas Fliit setl'd a' Port Jakson, Lieutenant [[Philip Gidley King]] got to Norfuk on Maach 6, 1788. Dis konwikt setlment laas entil 1814. A' fas setlment s' cos a' Royal Naewi want a' moo-oo fram a' ailen. A setlment duu laas lorng, cos a' moo-oo no gude f' shep. A' sekan konwikt setlment laas fram 1825-1855. Dieh setlment s' piinl setlment en em kondishans orn a ailen kaaduu. Em komandant s' behd. A' sekan setlment s' end en 1855 cos a' Yuunaited Kingd'm s' end transportieshan. Norfuk Ailen s' setld bai em Pitkernas o' Juun 6, 1856. Dem Pitkernas s' desend fram a' myuutenias o' HMS Baunti. In 1914, a' ailen se enkluud i' [[Ostrielya]] esa ekstirnal teritrii.

title: Tunisia
text:
Tunisia, ofisialii Repablik o' Tunisia (<a href="Erabek">Erabek</a>: تونس‎) esa kuntrii i' <a href="North%20Afreka">North Afreka</a>. T' kapitel citii es <a href="Tunis">Tunis</a> (Tunisia). A' es 163 610 km² area, an t' popyulayshun es 11,516,189 (2018). T' ofishol laenghwij es <a href="Erabek">Erabek</a> an t' ofishol kurencii es <a href="Dinar%20o%27%20Tunisia">Dinar o' Tunisia</a>. 
T' kuntrii bordas <a href="Algeria">Algeria</a> an <a href="Libiia">Libiia</a>. Big citiis apaat t' kapitel es <a href="Sfaaks">Sfaaks</a> an <a href="Souus">Souus</a>.

title: Hawayiian
text:
T' Hawayiian (Hawayiian: ʻŌlelo Hawaiʻi) esa laenghwij tal'n i' <a href="Hawayii">Hawayii</a> (<a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits</a>).

title: Moskou
text:
Moskou es t' <a href="Kapitel%20citii">kapitel</a> an' t' biges citii a' <a href="Rusha">Rusha</a> an' t' sekan biges citii a' <a href="Urup">Urup</a> (aftaa <a href="Istanbuel">Istanbuel</a>). T' popyulayshun, a' 2018 iya, s' es 12 506 468 salan. 
Histrei.
<a href="Yurii%20Vladimirovich%20Dolgorukii">Yurii Vladimirovich Dolgorukii</a>, t' knyaz (king) o' <a href="Kiev">Kiev</a>, faund'd Moskou i' 1147 iya. Afta, i' XIII—XV senchuriis Moskou wos t' kapitel citii a' <a href="Moskou%20Knyazhestvo">Moskou Knyazhestvo</a>. Et wos big citii o' dat tiem. I' 1605, Moskou wos attak'd b' <a href="Lzhedmitriy%20I">Lzhedmitriy I</a>, but hii wos kill'd. Dyuuriin' 1608—1610 iyas Moskou wos attak'd b' <a href="Lzhedmitriy%20II">Lzhedmitriy II</a>.
I' 1712, kapitel wos muuv'd from Moskou tuu <a href="Saint%20Piiterburg">Saint Piiterburg</a>. Butth i' Sovet tiem (1922—1991 iyas), Moskou bikaaem agaiin t' kapitel o' t' kuntrii. Afta <a href="YoSSR">YoSSR</a> kollaps'd Moskou bikaaem'd t' kapitel citii o' <a href="Rusha">Rusha</a>.
linked_text: Moskou es t' kapitel an' t' biges citii a' [[Rusha]] an' t' sekan biges citii a' [[Urup]] (aftaa [[Istanbuel]]). T' popyulayshun, a' 2018 iya, s' es 12 506 468 salan.  Histrei. Yurii Vladimirovich Dolgorukii, t' knyaz (king) o' [[Kiev]], faund'd Moskou i' 1147 iya. Afta, i' XIII—XV senchuriis Moskou wos t' kapitel citii a' Moskou Knyazhestvo. Et wos big citii o' dat tiem. I' 1605, Moskou wos attak'd b' Lzhedmitriy I, but hii wos kill'd. Dyuuriin' 1608—1610 iyas Moskou wos attak'd b' Lzhedmitriy II. I' 1712, kapitel wos muuv'd from Moskou tuu [[Saint Piiterburg]]. Butth i' Sovet tiem (1922—1991 iyas), Moskou bikaaem agaiin t' kapitel o' t' kuntrii. Afta [[YoSSR]] kollaps'd Moskou bikaaem'd t' kapitel citii o' [[Rusha]].

Kresmes (<a href="Anshunt%20Griik">Anshunt Griik</a>: Ή κατά σάρκα Γέννησις τού Κυρίου καί Θεού καί Σωτήρος ἡμῶν Ιησού Χριστού) es a <a href="Kreschenitii">Kreschen</a> ennyuual hohlidi dat silibriet d' biirth o' <a href="Jiisus%20Kraist">Jiisus Kraist</a>. Et s' silibriet'd orn <a href="Disemba%2025">Disemba 25</a> i' t' Werl eksept d' ortodoks kuntriis (<a href="Rusha">Rusha</a>, <a href="Yukrayn">Yukrayn</a>, <a href="Griis">Griis</a> andem) said et s' silibriet'd orn <a href="Jaenyuweri%207">Jaenyuweri 7</a>. Kresmes es orlsoe a kalcharl hohlidi f' plenti non-Kreschen salan.
Iin d' <a href="Northern%20Hemisfiir">Northern Hemisfiir</a>, d' Kresmes siisen es iin <a href="winta">winta</a>. Bifor et s' silibriet'd, enshunt salan silibriet'd defrent winta festeval, an sam o' em tradishn lorngf' et bekiem Kresmes tradishn. 
Dem Tradishn.
Pablik selebreyshun.
Plenti o' em sitiis an tauns silibreit Kresmes lorngf' putinap dekorayshuns.
linked_text: Kresmes (Anshunt Griik: Ή κατά σάρκα Γέννησις τού Κυρίου καί Θεού καί Σωτήρος ἡμῶν Ιησού Χριστού) es a [[Kreschen]] ennyuual hohlidi dat silibriet d' biirth o' Jiisus Kraist. Et s' silibriet'd orn Disemba 25 i' t' Werl eksept d' ortodoks kuntriis ([[Rusha]], [[Yukrayn]], [[Griis]] andem) said et s' silibriet'd orn Jaenyuweri 7. Kresmes es orlsoe a kalcharl hohlidi f' plenti non-Kreschen salan. Iin d' Northern Hemisfiir, d' Kresmes siisen es iin [[winta]]. Bifor et s' silibriet'd, enshunt salan silibriet'd defrent winta festeval, an sam o' em tradishn lorngf' et bekiem Kresmes tradishn.  Dem Tradishn. Pablik selebreyshun. Plenti o' em sitiis an tauns silibreit [[Kresmes]] lorngf' putinap dekorayshuns.

title: Wenezuela
text:
Wenezuela (ofisholi t' Bolivarian Repablik o' Wenezuela, <a href="Spanish">Spanish</a>: "República Bolivariana de Venezuela") esa kuntrii i' <a href="Sowth%20Merika">Sowth Merika</a>. T' kapitel an laarjist citii es <a href="Caracas">Caracas</a>.
T' teritrii o' Wenezuela was colonised bii <a href="Spain">Spain</a> i' 1522. Dis was i' spaait o' t' oposisyuun b' t' indijinuus piopel. I' 1811, Wenezuela biicame one o' t' first teritriis o' Hispanic Merika t' declare independens from Spain. Initially, howewer, et was konsaaider'd a part o' t' wider kuntrii <a href="Gran%20Colombia">Gran Colombia</a>. Gran Colombia collapsed i' 1831, an before daa a' fulii sovereign Wenezuela formed i' 1830.
I' t' 19t centurii, Wenezuela endured poliitical turmoil an militarii dictatorships. Dem lasted until t' mid-20t centurii, when there was a' transisyuun to demokrasii.
A' lack o' confidens i' t' <a href="Poliitical%20partii">poliitical partiis</a> o' t' time led to t' eleksyuun o' <a href="Hugo%20Ch%C3%A1vez">Hugo Chávez</a> i' 1998 (who was formerlii involved wi' a <a href="coup">coup</a>. Chávez would laanch t' <a href="Bolivarian%20Revolusyuun">Bolivarian Revolusyuun</a>, beginning wi' <a href="1999%20Wenezuelan%20konstitusyuun">rewriting t' konstitusyuun</a>. T' nyuu konstitusyuun renamed t' kuntrii ofisholii to t' "Bolivarian Repablik o' Wenezuela." Chávez established populist an leftist social an economic polisiis. His suksesor, <a href="Nicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro">Nicolás Maduro</a>, conitinued dem. Today, Wenezuela suffers from mass inflayshuun an povertii. T' oposisyuun blames dem i' t' policiis o' t' Revolusyuun.
I' 2019 t' liider o' the oposisyuun-kontrolled <a href="Nashyuunal%20Asemblii%20o%27%20Wenezuela">Nashyuunal Asemblii</a>, <a href="Juan%20Guaid%C3%B3">Juan Guaidó</a> was deklared bii t' oposisyuun t' bii Maduro's succesor. This was because dey claimed daa t' eleksyuun o' 2018 was fradulent. T' <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits</a>, <a href="Kolombiya">Kolombiya</a>, an mani othas rekognaaiz'd his claim. This has led to a' situasyuun i' which Wenezuela has two ofisholi rekognaaiz'd presidents.
linked_text: Wenezuela (ofisholi t' Bolivarian Repablik o' Wenezuela, [[Spanish]]: "República Bolivariana de Venezuela") esa kuntrii i' [[Sowth Merika]]. T' kapitel an laarjist citii es [[Caracas]]. T' teritrii o' Wenezuela was colonised bii [[Spain]] i' 1522. Dis was i' spaait o' t' oposisyuun b' t' indijinuus piopel. I' 1811, Wenezuela biicame one o' t' first teritriis o' Hispanic Merika t' declare independens from Spain. Initially, howewer, et was konsaaider'd a part o' t' wider kuntrii Gran Colombia. Gran Colombia collapsed i' 1831, an before daa a' fulii sovereign Wenezuela formed i' 1830. I' t' 19t centurii, [[Wenezuela]] endured poliitical turmoil an militarii dictatorships. Dem lasted until t' mid-20t centurii, when there was a' transisyuun to demokrasii. A' lack o' confidens i' t' poliitical partiis o' t' time led to t' eleksyuun o' Hugo Chávez i' 1998 (who was formerlii involved wi' a coup. Chávez would laanch t' Bolivarian Revolusyuun, beginning wi' rewriting t' konstitusyuun. T' nyuu konstitusyuun renamed t' kuntrii ofisholii to t' "Bolivarian Repablik o' Wenezuela." Chávez established populist an leftist social an economic polisiis. His suksesor, Nicolás Maduro, conitinued dem. Today, Wenezuela suffers from mass inflayshuun an povertii. title: Repablik o' Abkasiya
text:
Repablik o' Abkasiya (<a href="Abkasiyan">Abkasiyan</a>: "Аҧсны Аҳәынҭқарра") es unrekogniisid kuntrii to north o' <a href="Jorja">Jorja</a> (ofisholi et es part o' Jorja). T' kapitel citii es <a href="Sukhumi">Sukhumi</a> (Sukhum). T' ofisholi laenghwijes es <a href="Abkasiyan">Abkasiyan</a> an <a href="Rushan">Rushan</a>. 
5 kuntriis (<a href="Rusha">Rusha</a>, <a href="Nicaragua">Nicaragua</a>, <a href="Wenezuela">Wenezuela</a>, <a href="Nauruu">Nauruu</a> an <a href="Siriya">Siriya</a>) recoknisid independens o' Abkasiya.

title: Niue
text:
Niue esa <a href="Ailen">alien</a> kuntrii i' t' <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a>. Esa self-gawanin kuntrii i' frii Assosiayshun wi' <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a>. T' <a href="kapitel%20citii">kapitel citii</a> a' Niue es <a href="Alofi">Alofi</a>. Dem ofishol laenghwij a' t' ailen es Inglish an Niuean. Niue es 1624 km airea wi' a densitie a' 5.35/km^2. <a href="Niue%20Enternashunal%20Aeyaport">Niue Enternashunal Aeyaport</a> es t' wan aeyaport on t' alien an haufs fliits t' Auckland via "New Zealand Airlines". T' ofishol <a href="anthem%20o%27%20Niue">anthem o' Niue</a> es "Ko e Iki he Lagi".
Jiiografii.
Niue esa 269km^2 raysed koral atol i' t' Sowthern <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen,</a> eist a' <a href="Tonga">Tonga</a>. Dem jiiografiik co-ordinates ar 19°03′48″S 169°52′11″W. 
Niue es wan riili larj koral ailen an es wan a' t' larjes a' <a href="Erth">Erth.</a> Dem klif ar hi. 
Histrei.
Niue alien wos setl'd bei dem 'salan f' Samoa abaut 900 AD. Dem Tongan piopel setl'd Niue i' t' 16th centurii tuu. 
Kaptaan James Cook saw t' ailen i' 1774. Hii gaew t' niem "Savej Ailen" afta lanin' a' t' ailen b'cause t' piopel haed bluud a' dem bodis. Hii wos t' fas Urupean a' Niue tuu. 
Niue joyn'd t' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdom</a> i' 1901 afta' Kwiin Wiktoria gaew t' ailen permishun t' joyn.
Niue got independens i' 1994 b' t' Konstitushun a' Nyuu Ziilan. Robert Rex, a Urupean an Niuean wos t' fas Premier a' t' kuntrii. Hii wos Premier f' 18 yias.
Transportayshun.
Aeya.
<a href="Niue%20Enternashunal%20Aeyaport">Niue Enternashunal Aeyaport</a> es t' wan aeyaport a' t' alien an haufs fliits t' Auckland via "New Zealand Airlines". Dem fliits kam twiis per wiik. 
Lan.
Niue haufs a riin roed sistem tat konnekts t' toens o' t' ailen. 
See.
Niue haufs a port tat es yuus'd solii f' ankoraj.

title: Alofi
text:
Alofi es t' ofishol kapitel a' t' Pesifik ailen kuntrii o' <a href="Niue">Niue</a>. T' popyulayshun o' Alofi wos baut' 624 salan i' 2018 iya. T' wan aeyaport o' Niue Ailen, "<a href="Niue%20Enternashunal%20Aeyaport">Niue Enternashunal Aeyaport</a>", es sityuuaitid i' dis toen. Wit' a popyulayshun fewa den 1 000 salan, Alofi haufs t' distinktshun o' b'in t' sekan smaales nashunal kapitel i' form o' popyulayshun afta <a href="Ngerulmud">Ngerulmud</a>, t' kapitel citii o' <a href="Palau">Palau</a>. Et konsists o' tuu mien toens, <a href="Alofi%20North">Alofi North</a> an <a href="Alofi%20Sowth">Alofi Sowth</a>. 
Histrei.
I' t' Jaenyuweri o' 2004 yia, Niue wos hit b' t' larj tropikal stoem koel'd Cyclone Heta. Et kaus'd tuu piopel t' dii an meid ekstensiw damaj a' t' ailen. Mani o' dem bildings i' Alofi wos destroii'd, inkluden t' hospitel.

text:

title: Niuean
text: Niuean (Niuean: "ko e vagahau Niuē)" esa Polynesian laenghwij. Es rilii riilated t' <a href="Tongan">Tongan</a> an dem laenghwij lik <a href="Maori">Maaori</a>, <a href="Samoan">Samoaan</a>, an <a href="Hawaiian">Hawayiian</a> tuu. Abaut 8 000 piopel speik Niuean i' dem kuntrii lik <a href="Niue">Niue</a>, <a href="Dem%20Cook%20Ailen">Dem Cook Ailen</a>, <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a>, an <a href="Tonga">Tonga</a>.

title: Ofishol laenghwij
text: An Ofishol laenghwij es t' laenghwij us'd b' t' government a' a kuntrii. <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a> es wan a' t' larges ofishol laenghwijs a' <a href="Erth">Erth.</a> <a href="Spanish">Spanish</a> es a popwular ofishol laenghwij tuu. Es meinii tal'n i' <a href="Leten%20Merika">Leten Merika</a> an <a href="Spain">Spain</a>. <a href="French">French</a> es tal'n raun t' werl tuu, moslii i' formalii <a href="France">French</a> kolaniis lik parts a' west <a href="Afreka">Afreka</a>, <a href="Urup">Urup</a>, dem <a href="Indien%20Oshen">Indien</a> an de <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik</a> Oshen ailen, an mor. <a href="Rushan">Rushan</a> es popwulares laengwij a' <a href="Sentril%20Asya">Sentril Asya</a> an <a href="Eist%20Urup">Eist Urup</a>.

Es meinii tal'n i' [[Leten Merika]] an [[Spain]]. [[French]] es tal'n raun t' werl tuu, moslii i' formalii [[French]] kolaniis lik parts a' west [[Afreka]], [[Urup]], dem Indien an de Pesifik Oshen ailen, an mor. title: Dem Cook Ailen Maori
linked_text: <ns>0</ns>  <revision></revision>  <parentid>39436</parentid>  <timestamp>2019-03-26T16:01:58Z</timestamp>  <contributor></contributor>  <username>Xqbot</username>    <minor></minor>  <comment>Bot: Fixing double redirect to [[Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori]]; cosmetic changes</comment>  <model>wikitext</model>  <format>text/x-wiki</format> Ofishol Stetus. Dem [[Cook]] [[Ailen]] Māori b' kam a ofishol laenghwij o' dem [[Cook]] [[Ailen]] i' 2003, but haufs no ofishol stetus i' [[Nyuu Ziilan]], despiit t' fakt tat [[Nyuu Ziilan]] es signatorii t' t' Yunitid Nayshuns Declarayshun a' t' Riits o' Indijenus Piopels. Te Reo Maori Akt definishun. T' Te Reo Maori Act staits tat Māori: (sii ekstirnal links). Pukapukan es konsidired b' skolars an' talas tuu t' b' a distinkt laenghwij moor rilii riilated t' Sāmoan and Tokelauan t' Dem [[Cook]] [[Ailen]] Māori. Et b'longs t' t' Samoic subgroup o' t' Polynesian laenghwij family. T' intenshun b'hiind encludin' Pukapukan i' t' definishun o' Te Reo Maori wos t' meik shur o' ets protecshun. T' dialekts o' t' Iist Polynesian warietiis o' Dem [[Cook]] [[Ailen]] (colectivlii refirred t' as Dem [[Cook]] [[Ailen]] Māori) es: Dem Cook Ailen Māori es rilii relatid t' Tahitian an Nyuu Ziilan Māori, an deir es a degrii o' mushual intelijibilitii wit' both o' dese laenghwijs. T' laenghwij es teoreticalii regulatid b' t' "Kopapa Reo" meik'd i' 2003, but dis organisayshun es currentlii dorment. Writin sistem an pronunsiayshun. Deir esa debait o' t' stendardisayshun o' t' writin sistem. Altho t' usaj o' t' macron (־) "te makarona" an t' glottel stawp "amata" (ꞌ) (/ʔ/) es recommendid, most talas don't use t' tuu diakritiks i' dail writin'. Dem Cook Ailen Māori Revis'd Nyuu Testament uses a stendardis'd ortografii (spellin sistem) tat encludes t' diakritiks wen dey're fonemic but nor elsabout. Gramma. Dem [[Cook]] [[Ailen]] Māori es an isolatin laenghwij [[wit]]' a rilii smaal morfolojii. Kaas es mark'd b' t' partikul tat inishiaits a nown frase, an lik most o' dem Iist Polynesian laenghwijs, dem Cook [[Ailen]] Māori haufs nominativ-accusativ kas markin. T' unmark'd konstituent orduh es predicait inishul. Tat es, werb inishul i' werbal frases an nominal-predicaot inishul i' non-werbal frases.

title: Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori
text:
Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori esa Iistern Polynesian language. Ets t' ofishol laenghwij o' dem Cook Ailen an esa indijenus laenghwij o' t' Realm o' <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a>. Dem Cook Ailen Māori es rilii riilated t' <a href="Maori">Nyuu Ziilan Maaori</a> but es wan laenghwij. Dem Cook Ailen Māori es simplii kaul'd Māori wen deir es no niid t' disambigyuait et f' Nyuu Ziilan Maaori, but ets known as Māori Kūki 'Āirani (o Maori Kuki Airani), o, controvershulii, Rarotongan, tuu. Mani o' dem Kuuk Ailendas also kaul et "Te reo Ipukarea", literalii "t' laenghwij o' t' Ansestral Hoemlan".
Ofishol Stetus.
Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori b' kam a ofishol laenghwij o' Dem Kuuk Ailen i' 2003, but haufs no ofishol stetus i' Nyuu Ziilan, despiit t' fakt tat Nyuu Ziilan es signatorii t' t' Yunitid Nayshuns Declarayshun a' t' Riits o' Indijenus Piopels.
Te Reo Maori Akt definishun.
T' <a href="http%3A//www.paclii.org/ck/legis/num_act/trma2003130/">Te Reo Maori Act</a> staits tat Maaori: 
(sii ekstirnal links).
Pukapukan es konsidir'd b' skolars an' talas tuu t' b' a distinkt laenghwij moor rilii riilated t' Sāmoan and Tokelauan t' Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori. Et b'longs t' t' Samoic subgroup o' t' Polynesian laenghwij family. T' intenshun b'hiind encludin' Pukapukan i' t' definishun o' Te Reo Maori wos t' meik shur o' ets protecshun.
Dem dialekts o' t' Iist Polynesian warietiis o' Dem Kuuk Ailen (colectivlii refirr'd t' as Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori) ar:

T' laenghwij es teoreticalii regulatid b' t' "Kopapa Reo" meik'd i' 2003, but dis organisayshun es currentlii dorment.
Writin sistem an pronunsiayshun.
Deir esa debait o' t' stendardisayshun o' t' writin sistem. Alla t' yuusej a' t' macron (־) "te makarona" an t' glottel stawp "amata" (ꞌ) (/ʔ/) es rekommendid, mos talas don't yuus t' tuu diakritiks i' dialii writin. Dem <a href="http%3A//bibles.org/rar-CIMRNT/Matt/1">Cook Ailen Māori Revis'd Nyuu Testament</a> yuuses a stendardis'd ortografii (spellin sistem) tat encludes t' diakritiks wen dey're fonemic but nor elsabout.
Gramma.
Dem Cook Ailen Māori es an isolatin laenghwij wit' a rilii smaal morfolojii. Kaas es mark'd b' t' partikul tat inishiaits a nown frase, an lik most o' dem Iist Polynesian laenghwijs, dem Cook Ailen Māori haufs nominativ-accusativ kas markin.
T' unmark'd konstituent orduh es predicait inishul. Tat es, werb inishul i' werbal frases an nominal-predicaot inishul i' non-werbal frases.

title: Fijian
text:
Fijian (Fijian: "") esa Austronesian laenghwij o' t' Malayo-Polynesian family tal'n b' soom 350 000–450 000 etnik Fijians as a natiw laenghwij. T' 2013 Konstitushun maeked Fijian as an ofishol laenghwij o' <a href="Fiijii">Fiji</a>, wit' I<a href="Inglish">nglish</a> an <a href="Hindi">Hindi</a> tuu, an deir es diskushun abaut establishin et as t' "nashunal laenghwij", alla Inglish an Hindi wil stey ofishol. Fijian esa VOS laenghwij.
Stendard Fijian es bais'd a' t' talin' o' Bau, wich esa Iist Fijian laenghwij.
A pidjiniz'd form es used b' mani Indo-Fijians an etnik Chinese a' dem ailen, whiil Pidgin Hindustani es used b' mani rural etnik Fijians.
Fonolojii.
T' consonant fonemes o' Fijian es as shown i' t' followin tabul:
T' consonent writ'n ⟨dr⟩ haufs bin describ'd as a prenasaliz'd trill [nr] o trill'd fricativ [ndr]. Tho, ets onli rarlii pronouns'd wit' a trill'd reliis; t' primarii feachure distinguishin et f' ⟨d⟩ es tat ets postalveolar, [ɳɖ], insteado' dental/alveolar.
T' sowns [p] an [f] okkur onli i' loanwords f' otha laenghwijs. T' sowns [x] an [h] onli okkur f' talas f' serten rejins o' t' kuntrii.
Notis t' differens i' place o' articulayshun b'twiin t' voic'd-voiceles fricativ payrs: bilabial [β] vs. labiodental [f], an dental [ð] vs. alveolar [s].

title: Nauruuan
text:
Nauruuan ulla Nauru<ref name="ISO 639-2/RA"></ref><ref name="ISO 639-3/RA"></ref> (Nauruuan: "Dorerin Naoero") esa <a href="Osheania">Osheaniik</a> laenghwij, tal'n nativlii b' abaut 6 000 piopel i' t' ailen kuntrii o' <a href="Nauruu">Nauru</a>. Ets relayshunship tuu t' taedha Mikroneyshun laenghwijs es nor understood wel.
Fonolojii.
Consonents.
Nauruan haufs 16–17 consonant fonemes. Nauruan meiks fonemic kontrasts b'twiin welariz'd an palataliz'd labial consonants. Welarisayshun es nor wisibul b'foor lon bak wowels an palatalisyshun es nor wisibul b'foor nor-lo frunt wowels.
Voiceless stawps es geminat'd an dem naysal also kontrast i' lonness. Dental stawps /t/ an /d/ b'kam [tʃ] an [dʒ] respectivlii b'foor dem hi frunt wowel.

title: Moriori
text:
Moriori esa Polynesian laenghwij mos rilii riilated t' <a href="Maaori">Nyuu Ziilan Maaori</a>. Ets natiw laenghwij o' dem Moriori, t' endijenus piopel o' dem <a href="Chattam%20Ailen">Chattam Ailen</a> (Moriori: "Rēkohu") — an arkipelago o' <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a>, sowth iist o' Nyuu Ziilan's Sowth Ailen. T' las spiika wos <a href="Hirawanu%20Tapu">Hirawanu Tapu</a>.
Histrei.
Dem Chatham Ailen's fas Yuripiin kontakt wos lorngf' William R. Broughton o' t' Yunitid Kingdum huu lan'd a' 29 Nowemba 1791 an klaim'd dem ailen. Hii reniem'd hiis shep, HMS "Chetem". Broughton's shep salan intaamerii'd lorngf' dem laaidiis o' Moriori.
T' enwayshun f' Taranaaki haufd a hewii empakt a' Moriori popyulayshun, kulchur an laenghwij, lorngf' onli 101 Moriori steyin i' 1862, an few tork'n t' laenghwij b' t' 1870s. Tho, Samuel Deighton, Resident Magistrate a' dem Chathams f' 1873 t' 1891, complii'd a short wokabyularii o' dem Moriori werd, lorngf' deir ekwiwalents i' Māori an Inglish. T' wokabyularii wos publish'd as an appendiks o' Michael King's "Moriori: A Salan Rediiscower'd".
T' big kilin o' t' Moriori salan okkur'd durin t' fawl o' 1835. T' enwayshun o' dem Chatham Ailen left dem Moriori salan an deir kulchur t' dy of. Dos huu surwiiw'd wos iider kept as slaaws o t' Moriori wer wetls wos nor saankshun'd t' marrii otha Moriori o hauf letl salan wit'i' deir raas. Dis kaus'd deir salan an deir laenghwij t' b' endanjer'd. Deir wos onli 101 Moriori salan left outta 2 000 huu haufd surwiiw'd i' 1863.
T' laenghwij wos riimeik'd f' Barry Barclay's 2000 film dokumentarii "T' Featas o' Piis", i' a riimeikin o' Moriori kontakt lorngf' Pākehā an Māori.
I' 2001, as paat o' a kulchural riiwiwal moowment, Moriori piopel b'gan attempts t' riiwiwe t' laenghwij, an kompiil'd a daatabeis o' dem Moriori werd. Deya esa POLLEX (Polynesian Lexicon Project Online) daatabeis o' dem Moriori werd tuu.
T' 2006 Nyuu Ziilan sens's show'd 945 salan choosin t' include "Moriori" amonst deya traib'l affiliayshuns, compar'd t' 35 salan i' t' 1901 sens's.
Klasifikayshun.
Wan hipotesis tat wos diskredited i' t' 1960s an 1970s staited dem Moriori salan wos distinkt f' dem Māori set'las o' Nyuu Ziilan, an anotha hipotesis amon dem aarkaeolojists huu biiliew'd tat dem Moriori piopel huu set'l'd a' dem Chatham Ailen wos orijinalii Māori.
T' jiiniaalojikel histrei o' t' Moriori laenghwij ekspooses t' Proto-tahitic subgroup tat separaits i't' dem for laenghwijs: Tahitian, Rarotongan, Tuamotuan, an Māori. Moriori es konsidired a dialekt o' Maori. Dem tuu laenghwij shar a riilated fonolojikal form.

T' wokabyularii wos publish'd as an appendiks o' [[Michael King's]] "Moriori: [[A]] Salan Rediiscower'd". T' big kilin o' t' Moriori salan okkur'd durin t' fawl o' 1835. T' enwayshun o' dem Chatham [[Ailen]] left dem Moriori salan an deir kulchur t' dy of. Dos huu surwiiw'd wos iider kept as slaaws o t' Moriori wer wetls wos nor saankshun'd t' marrii otha Moriori o hauf letl salan wit'i' deir raas. Dis kaus'd deir salan an deir laenghwij t' b' endanjer'd. Deir wos onli 101 Moriori salan left outta 2 000 huu haufd surwiiw'd i' 1863. T' laenghwij wos riimeik'd f' [[Barry Barclay's]] 2000 film dokumentarii "T' Featas o' Piis", i' a riimeikin o' Moriori kontakt lorngf' Pākehā an Māori. I' 2001, as paat o' a kulchural riiwiwal moowment, Moriori piopel b'gan attempts t' riiwiwe t' laenghwij, an kompiil'd a daatabeis o' dem Moriori werd. Deya esa POLLEX (Polynesian Lexicon [[Project]] Online) daatabeis o' dem Moriori werd tuu. T' 2006 [[Nyuu Ziilan]] sens's show'd 945 salan choosin t' include "Moriori" amonst deya traib'l affiliayshuns, compar'd t' 35 salan i' t' 1901 sens's. Klasifikayshun. Wan hipotesis tat wos diskredited i' t' 1960s an 1970s staited dem Moriori salan wos distinkt f' dem Māori set'las o' [[Nyuu Ziilan]], an anotha hipotesis amon dem aarkaeolojists huu biiliew'd tat dem Moriori piopel huu set'l'd a' dem [[Chatham]] [[Ailen]] wos orijinalii Māori. T' jiiniaalojikel histrei o' t' Moriori laenghwij ekspooses t' Proto-tahitic subgroup tat separaits i't' dem for laenghwijs: Tahitian, Rarotongan, Tuamotuan, an Māori. Moriori es konsidired a dialekt o' Maori. Dem tuu laenghwij shar a riilated fonolojikal form.

title: Kapa
text:
Capparis spinosa, t' kapa stik, elsa kaul'd Flindas rouus, esa perennial plaant daa biers round'd, fleshii liifs an larj wiit t' pinkish-wiit flowas.
T' plaant es best nouun f' t' wekl o' em flowa buds (kapers), uulii yuus'd as' a seasonin, an t' fruit (kapa berriis), both o' wich es yuushuallii eat'n pikl'd. Otha species o' "Capparis" es elsa pik'd alon wit' "C. spinosa" f' deir buds o' fruuets. Taedha paats o' "Capparis" plaants es yuus'd i' t' manyufakchurin o' em medisiins an kosmetiks.

title: Marseii
text:
Marseii (<a href="French">French</a>: Marseille) esa t' sekan biges citii i' <a href="France">France</a>. T' popyulayshun a' 2015 iya esa 869 815 piopel.
Histrei.
Marseii wos faund'd i' 600 iya BCE b' <a href="Griese">Grieks</a> as a' Massalia. Massalia becaam'd an endependent kuntrii an wos an alli o' Rome. Thaan b' Massalia wos faund'd <a href="Nizza">Nizza</a>, <a href="Antiib">Antiib</a>, <a href="Avinion">Avinion</a> andem. I' 1481 iya t' citii wos t' paat o' France. 
I' XVIII cenchurii mor den 70% o' t' popyulayshun o' citii wos daiied b'cause o' t' playg.

title: Vichii France
text:
Vichii Frans (<a href="French">French</a>: "Régime de Vichy") e t' kommon niem f' t' French Stait ("État français"), led b' Marshul Philippe Pétain durin <a href="Werld%20War%20II">Werl War II</a>. Ewacyuatid f' Paris t' Vichii i' t' unokyupy'd "Frii Zon" ("zone libre") i' t' sowthern paat a' metropoliten <a href="France">France</a> wich encludid French <a href="Algeria">Aljeria</a>, et stey'd responsibul f' t' siwil administrayhun a' France an t' French kolonyal empire tuu.
Owuhwiew.
I' 1940 iya, Marshal Pétain wos known as a Fas Werl War herow, t' vikta o' t' battel o' Verdun. As t' las premier o' t' Tird Republik, bein a riiakshunarii b' enclinayshun, hi blaim'd t' Tird Republik's demokrasii f' Frans' sudden defiit b' Doichland. Hi set'dap a paternalistik, autoritarien reygim tat aktivlii kolaboratid lorngf' <a href="Doichland">Doichland</a>, Vichii's ofishol neutralitii nor lorngf' stanin'. T' Vichii gawanment kooperaytid lorngf' dem Nazis' rayshul policiis.
A' 11 November 1942, followin' t' lanin' a' dem Allis i' <a href="North%20Afreka">North Afreka</a> (Operayshun Toorch), dem Aksis launch'd Operayshun Anton, okyupyin' sowthern France an disbandin 'e striktlii limitid "Armistice Armii" tat Vichii haufd bin alow'd b' t' armistice.

title: Etlantida
text: Etlantida (<a href="Anshunt%20Griik">Anshunt Griik</a>: Ἀτλαντὶς) esa fikshyunal ailen kuntrii menshyun'd b' <a href="Plato">Plato</a>, <a href="Herodotuus">Herodotuus</a>, <a href="Diodorus%20Sicillian">Diodorus Sicillian</a>. Et wos popyulayt'd b' Etlants but i' 9500 iya BCE a' ailen saank'd as a' resuult o' an' erthkuaak. As a Plato's deskripshun, Etlantida wos sityuaitiid bitwiin mautiin chain <a href="Etlas">Etlas</a> i' <a href="Afreka">Afreka</a> an <a href="Jibrulta">Jibrulta</a>. Et es a' prototiip o' t' ailen <a href="Utopia">Utopia</a> deskraiib'd b' <a href="Tomas%20Moor">Tomas Moor</a> an o' t' ailen <a href="Bensalem">Bensalem</a> deskraiib'd i' buuk <a href="Nyuu%20Atlantis">"Nyuu Atlantis"</a> b' <a href="Fransiis%20Baikon">Fransiis Baikon</a>.

title: Tokelau
linked_text: Tokelau esa dapendint teritrii o' Nyuu Ziilan i' t' sowthern Pesifik Oshen. Et konsist a' trii tropikal koral atols (Atafu, Nukunonu an Fakaofo), wit' a kombin'd lan airea a' 10 km2 (4 sq mi). T' kapitel rotaits yialii b'twiin dem trii atols. Tokelau lys north o' dem Samoan Ailen, iist o' Tuwaluu, sowth o' dem Phoenix Ailen, sowthwest o' dem mor distent Line Ailen, an northwest o' dem Cook Ailen. Swains Ailen es jiiografikalii par o' Tokelau, but es subjekt t' a kurrent teritrorial dispuut an es kurentlii amminister'd b' dem Yunitid Staits as par o' Merikan Samoa. Tokelau haufs a popyulayshun a' aproksimatelii 1503 piopel, t' forth-smaales popyulayshun a' eni sowyern stait o dependsii. As a' t' 2019 census, abaut 48%o' dem piopel i' [[Tokelau]] wer born i' an otha kuntrii, mostlii i' [[Samoa]] an [[Nyuu Ziilan]]. T' kuntrii haufs a lif ekspansatii a' 69, komparable [[wit]]' otha Oceanian ailen kuntriis. Aproksimatelii 94% a' t' popyulayshun tal Tokelauan as a fas laenghwij. T' kuntrii haufs t' smaales ekonomii i' t' werl, alla ets a liida i' renyuuable enerjii, b'in t' fas 100% sola power'd nayshun i' t' werld. T' motto a' [[Tokelau]] es "[[Tokelau]] mo te Atua", wich miins "[[Tokelau]] f' t' Almitii."

title: Entanashunal Fonetikl Elphabet
text:
Entanashunal Fonetikl Elphabet (EFE; <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a>: IPA; <a href="French">French</a>: API) esa elphabetik system o' fonetikl notayshun beis'd a' t' <a href="Leten">Leten</a> elphabet. Et wos devais'd b' t' <a href="Entanashunal%20Fonetikl%20Assoshiayshun">Entanashunal Fonetikl Assoshiayshun</a> i' t' end o' 19th cenchurii. T' EFE es yuus'd b' styuudents, akters, singaas, linguists andem.
Deya esa 163 o' em symbols a' EFE: 107 symbols-lettas, 52 symbols-diakritiks an 4 prosodiis (2005).

title: Hawayii
text: Hawayii esa ailen stait o' dem <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits</a>. Ets t' 50th an mos resent stait t' hauf joyn dem Yunitid Staits, haufin resiiv'd staithood a' 21 Orgas 1959. Hawayii es t' onlii Y.S. stait loekaytid i' <a href="Osheania">Osheania</a>, t' onlii Y.S. stait loekaytid outsayd <a href="North%20Merika">North Merika</a>, an t' onlii wan kompoz'd entirelii o' ailen. Ets t' northernmos ailen gruup i' Poliinesya, okyupayin' moos o' an arkipelago i' t' sentril <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a>. T' stait enkompases nearlii t' wolkaynik Hawayiian arkipelago i' daffy, wich komprises hundreds a' ailen spred owa 2 400 km. A' t' sowthiistern end a' t' arkipelago, dem ietth mien ailen ar—i' orda f' northwest t' sowthiist: <a href="Niihau">Niihau</a>, <a href="Kauayii">Kauayii</a>, <a href="Oahu">Oahu</a>, <a href="Molokayii">Molokayii</a>, <a href="Lanayii">Lanayii</a>, <a href="Kahoolawe">Kahoolawe</a>, <a href="Mauyii">Mauyii</a>, an t' Ailen a' Hawayii. T' las es t' larjes ailen i' t' gruup; ets often kaul'd t' "Larj Ailen" o "Hawayii Ailen" t' awoid konfushun wit' t' stait o arkipelago. T' arkipelago es fisiiografikalii an etnolojikalii part o' t' Polynesian subriijen a' Osheania.

Ets t' northernmos ailen gruup i' Poliinesya, okyupayin' moos o' an arkipelago i' t' sentril [[Pesifik Oshen]]. T' stait enkompases nearlii t' wolkaynik Hawayiian arkipelago i' daffy, wich komprises hundreds a' ailen spred owa 2 400 km. A' t' sowthiistern end a' t' arkipelago, dem ietth mien ailen ar—i' orda f' northwest t' sowthiist: Niihau, Kauayii, Oahu, Molokayii, Lanayii, Kahoolawe, Mauyii, an t' Ailen a' Hawayii. T' las es t' larjes ailen i' t' gruup; ets often kaul'd t' "Larj Ailen" o "Hawayii Ailen" t' awoid konfushun wit' t' stait o arkipelago. T' arkipelago es fisiiografikalii an etnolojikalii part o' t' Polynesian subriijen a' Osheania.

title: Motto
text: A motto esa maksim; a frays ment t' formallii summaryz t' mien motiwayshun o entenshun a' a sala, family, soshul gruup o organizayshun. Mottos ar yuushulii found predominantlii i' writ'n form (nor lik slogans, wich mei alsuh b' ekspress'd orallii), an mei stem f' lon tradishuns a' soshul foundayshuns, o f' signifikent iwents, such as a sivil war o a revolushun. A motto mei b' i' eni laenghiwj, but Latin haufs b'n waidlii yuus'd, espeshulii i' t' Western werl.

title: Merikan Samoa
text:
Merikan Samoa esa unenkorparaytid teritrii o' dem <a href="Yunitid%20Staits">Yunitid Staits</a> loekaytid i' t' Sowth <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a>, sowthiist a' <a href="Samoa">Samoa</a>. Ets loekayshun es senta'd aroun 14.2710° S, 170.1322° W. Ets a' t' iistern borda o' t' Entanashunal Dait Liin. Endapendint Samoa es west a' et.
Merikan Samoa konsist o' fyv mien ailen an tuu koral attoels. T' larjes an mos popyulus ailen es <a href="Tutuila">Tutuila</a>, wit' dem <a href="Manu%CA%BBa%20Ailen">Manuʻa Ailen</a>, <a href="Rouus%20Attoel">Rouus Attoel</a>, an <a href="Swains%20Ailen">Swains Ailen</a> also enkluded i' t' teritrii. All o' dem ailen eksept f' Swains Ailen ar part o' dem Samoan Ailen, loekaytid west o' <a href="Dem%20Kuuk%20Ailen">Dem Kuuk Ailen</a>, north o' <a href="Tonga">Tonga</a>, an soom 300 miles (500 km) sowth o' Tokelau. T' t' west ar dem ailen o' t' Wallis an Futuna gruup.
T' kurrent popyulayshun o' Merikan Samoa es aaproksimantlii 55,689 piopel. Mos a' dem ar "nashunals but nor citiizens o' dem Yunitid Staits a' birth". Mos Merikan Samoans ar tal tuu laenghwij an ken tal <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a> an <a href="Samoaan">Samoaan</a> flyuuentlii. Samoan es t' saim laenghwij tal'n i' neyborin endapendint Samoa.

title: Atafu
text: Atafu es t' kapitel o' <a href="Tokelau">Tokelau</a>. Akordin t' t' 2016 yia census, 541 piopel off liiw a' Atafu (alla jes' 413 wer presan a' census nyt). A' dos presan, 78% belon t' t' Congregayshunal Kirch. T' mien setalmen a' t' atol es loekaytid a' Atafu Ailen a' t' northwestern korna a' t' atol. T' Presbyterian Kirch wos establish'd a' t' ailen i' 1858 yia, but teda almos all a' dem residents belon t' t' Congregayshunal Kreschen Kirch. T' fas toen a' Atafu wos establish'd a' t' sowthern part a' t' islet, an dem residents maeked hauses alon t' laguun shor t' reciiw dem koolin traid winds.

title: Dem Kuuk Ailen
text:
Kuuk Ailens/Dem Kuuk Ailen (<a href="Dem%20Cook%20Ailen%20M%C4%81ori">Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori</a>: "Kūki 'Āirani", <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a>: "Cook Islands") esa self-gawanin ailen kuntrii i' t' Sowth <a href="Pesifik%20Oshen">Pesifik Oshen</a> i' frii assosiayshun lorngf' <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a>. Ets kompos'd a' 15 ailen huus lan airea i' daffy es 240 sq kilometres (92.7 sq mi). Dem Kuuk Ailen Eksklusiw Iikonomik Soen (EIS) kowas 1 800 000 sq kilometres (690 000 sq mi) a' oshen. T' kapitel o' Dem Kuuk Ailen es <a href="Awarua">Awarua</a>, det es orn t' ailen a' <a href="Rarotonga">Rarotonga</a>.
Nyuu Ziilan es riisponsibel f' Dem Kuuk Ailens' defens an entanashunal riilaeshensheps, alla, dem ar eksersis'd i' konsyulayshun wit' Dem Kuuk Ailen. I' riisent tiems, Dem Kuuk Ailen hauf edoptid an enkriisinglii endapendint entanashunal polisii. Alla Dem Kuuk Ailenas ar sitizens a' Nyuu Ziilan, dem hauf t' status a' dem Kuuk Ailen nashunals, wich es nor giwen t' otha Nyuu Ziilan sitizens.

title: Okhrid
text:

I' 1989/1980 iyas Okhrid an Okhrid's Leik wos akseptiid t' Kulchural and Naachural Woral Heritaidj Saats b' <a href="YNESKO">YNESKO</a>.
Demografieks.
As a' 2002 iya i' Okhrid deir wos 42 033 piopel.

title: Hirawanu Tapu
text: Hirawanu Tapu (1824 — 1900) wos a' notibl liida o' Moriori nayshunalitii (i' <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a>), t' las spiika o' t' <a href="Moriori%20laenghwij">Moriori laenghwiji</a>. Hii wos barn i' t' willaj <a href="Te%20Apawatiki">Te Apawatiki</a> o' <a href="dem%20Chattam%20Ailen">dem Chattam Ailen</a>. Hii wos t' major suurs f' <a href="Aleksandar%20Shand">Aleksandar Shand's</a> werks 'bout Moriori <a href="histrei">histrei</a>, <a href="laenghwij">laenghwij</a>, <a href="kulchur">kulchur</a> andem. 'Bout 90% o' orl ikstaant informayshun a' salan o' hiis nayshunalitii paas'd thruu hiis harns.

title: Harn
text: Harn esa wan paat o' <a href="bodii">bodii</a>, t' end o' <a href="aarm">aarm</a>, an ets a' <a href="prehensilitii">prehensilitii</a>. Uni <a href="Praimat">praimats</a> sach as <a href="Hyuuman">hyuumans</a>, <a href="Chimpansii">chimpansiis</a>, <a href="Mankii">mankiis</a>, <a href="Lemuur">lemuurs</a> hauf t' harn, but deir esa saam ekslyushens: <a href="koalas">koalas</a>, <a href="Rakuun">rakuuns</a> andem. T' hyuuman harn normallii haufs 4 <a href="Finga">fingas</a> an a <a href="tuumb">tuumb</a>. Et haufs 27 bouns, nor inkluden t' <a href="sesamoiid%20boun">sesamoiid boun</a>, t' namba o' wich wariies b'twiin piopel.

title: Pinsk
text:
Pinsk (<a href="Belerushan">Belerushan</a>: "Пінск"; <a href="Rushan">Rushan</a>: "Пинск") esa citii i' <a href="Belerus">Belerus</a>. Ets kulchural an' indastriyal sentaa o' <a href="Polesie">Polesie</a>. T' popyulayshun a' 2018 iya esa 137 961 salan.
Jiografii.
T' jiografiikel sentaa o' Pinsk es a' 186 km west a' <a href="Brest">Brest</a>, an' a' 304 km sowthiist a' <a href="Minsk">Minsk</a>. Et es sityuuaytiid a' rivehs <a href="Pina">Pina</a> an' <a href="Pripyat">Pripyat</a>. Terraiin a' Pinsk esa rade flaet. Kuwaa a' airea a' 47.36 km2 (4736 ha). 
Tiemsoen a' Pinsk es (Minsk Tiem). 
Klaaimat es kontenentl. Et haufs maild <a href="winta">winta</a> an' woom <a href="sama">sama</a>. I' Pinsk deir esa manii parks an' skves. Lanskeeip konsists f' willajes, lekl forests, rivehs an' laeks.

title: Topfriidum
text:
Topfriidum esa raait o' women t' bii wit nor <a href="shirt">shirt</a> an <a href="bra">bra</a> (<a href="topless">toples</a>) i' em pablik plaeses daa men ar allaud tuu. Ets konsaaider'd t' bii a' <a href="Feminism">feminist</a> muuwment. Elsa, topfriidum advokaiits t' raait t' briistfiid i' pablik. 
T' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdum</a>, <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits o' Merika</a>, <a href="Kaneda">Kaneda</a>, an otha kuntriis hauf lous daa ban <a href="diskriminayshun">diskriminayshun</a> basiid a' t' genda. Despaait dis, saam Merikan staits still hauf lous daa say a' woman's <a href="Briist">briists</a> ar <a href="indeseent%20iksposhuur">indeseent iksposhuur</a>, an iivn i' kuntriis laaik Kaneda where ers legal f' women t' shouu deir briists i' pablik, sosietii's standarts miek dem fiil laaik dem ken nor.
Argyuuments.
For.
Advokaiits o' topfriidum argyuu daa es nor akseptable t' hauf a' difrent set o' standarts f' women. Manii kuntriis hauf lous daa ban diskriminayshun basiid a' t' genda. Advokaiits i' dem kuntriis argyuu daa topfriidum es protekted unda t' lou.
Against.
Manii sosietiis argyuu daa dem femaiil briists ar indeesent. Dem konsaaider daa dem briists o' a' woman ar sekshul i' natur an biikaus o' dis dem argyuu that dem briists must stay cowered. Elsa, dem sosietiis aften hauf relijiious wyuus as justification.
Legalitii.
Femaiils biin toples i' pablik plaesiis es allaud b' t' lous o' manii kuntriis a' <a href="Urup">Urup</a>. I' saam kuntriis ivn i' Urup ets nor socially accepted though. Scandinavian lous an wyuus ar musa aeksepten o' t' praektis. T' kuntrii <a href="Iseland">Iseland</a> es said b' manii piopel t' bii t' mas feminist kuntrii i' Erth.
Saam kuntriis hauf lous daa say dis es nor legal. Dem tend t' hauf musa konservatiiv kulturs, but saam Western sosietiis (lik t' Yunited Staits) elsa hauf lous against toplesnes. Certain kuntriis i' t' <a href="Medl%20Eist">Medl Eist</a> hauf lous daa based on <a href="Islem">Islem</a> hauf entapreteyshuns o' t' <a href="Qu%27ran">Qu'ran</a> (Islem's holy buuk) that say a woman must cover her entire body. Such religious views ar then made t' lou. 
<a href="Endya">Endya</a> is elsa a musa relijiious kuntrii. Dem hauf wyuus daa konsaaider toplessness t' bii nyuuditii, an dem konsaaider nyuuditii bad.
But elsa certain Western kuntriis hauf lous against toplessness, notably certain Merican staits, lik said above.

Elsa, topfriidum advokaiits t' raait t' briistfiid i' pablik.  T' [[Yunitid Kingdum]], [[Yunitid Staits o' Merika]], [[Kaneda]], an otha kuntriis hauf lous daa ban diskriminayshun basiid a' t' genda. Despaait dis, saam Merikan staits still hauf lous daa say a' woman's briists ar indeseent iksposhuur, an iivn i' kuntriis laaik Kaneda where ers legal f' women t' shouu deir briists i' pablik, sosietii's standarts miek dem fiil laaik dem ken nor. Advokaiits i' dem kuntriis argyuu daa topfriidum es protekted unda t' lou. Against. Manii sosietiis argyuu daa dem femaiil briists ar indeesent. Dem konsaaider daa dem briists o' a' woman ar sekshul i' natur an biikaus o' dis dem argyuu that dem briists must stay cowered. Elsa, dem sosietiis aften hauf relijiious wyuus as justification. Legalitii. Femaiils biin toples i' pablik plaesiis es allaud b' t' lous o' manii kuntriis a' [[Urup]]. I' saam kuntriis ivn i' Urup ets nor socially accepted though. Scandinavian lous an wyuus ar musa aeksepten o' t' praektis. T' kuntrii [[Iseland]] es said b' manii piopel t' bii t' mas feminist kuntrii i' Erth. Saam kuntriis hauf lous daa say dis es nor legal. But [[elsa]] certain Western kuntriis hauf lous against toplessness, notably certain Merican staits, lik said above.

title: Bra
text:
Bra esa andargamn f' holdin dem briists o' women in plaes, an' kiip dem kover'd. Bras ar design'd f' wiid warietiis o' purposes, such a' enhans t' size o' dem briists, t' criiate kliiwaj, among otha konsaaiderashuns. I' adishun t' tuu kups, a' bra normalii haa four bands. 
Sum piopel haa a' medikal niid f' bras, but t' majoritii wear dem f' feshn o' kulchural riisons onlii. Deir esn't ewidens daa bras prewen t' saggin o' dem briists w' aging; aksyulii t' ewidens i' kontrarii. One studieh sujests daa bras wiiken t' tissue o' dem briists, w' eksepshun o' durin eksersiis o' sports.
Bras ar eften yuus'd b' women t' enhans deir figure, an' help dem achiif deir ideal bodii figyur. Dem haa biikom a' feshn trend.
I' spaait o' dis, manii women haa protest'd t' standart o' sosietii daa women must wear bras a' aw tiems i' plaeses o' pablik. Dem haa protest'd dem rules o' schools an' workplaeses daa require women t' wear garments o' support. A' earlii a' 1873, t' author Elizabeth Stuart Phelps advokaait'd daa women burn deir bras.
Kulchur.
Feshn.
T' choice about waa bra t' wear i' influuens'd b' soshul persepsyuns o' ideal fiimale bodii shape. One riison why women wear bras es f' seks appeal. Bras ken elsa bii yuus'd t' miek a' soshul statement.
A' dem 1920s i' dem <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits o' Merika</a>, t' feshn a' tiem waa miek dem briists look flat. Durin dem 1940s an' 1950s, t' "sweater girl" biikam feshnabl, support'd b' "bullet bra." A' dem earlii 1960s smawer briists waa mor popyular, an' a' dem 1990s, larjer briists waa t' trend. A' outerwear, bras i' form o' bikini tops biikam t' norm a' dem modern tiems.
Victoria's Secret mieks a' fantasii bra ewery autumn. A' 2003 dem hired t' jeweler Mouawad t' kriiat one yuusin ower 2500 karats o' diemonds an' safires. A' US$10 million w' most ekspensif bra a' werl a' tiem.
Andargamn a' outerwear.
T' sports bra waa first inwented a' 1975. Women wor dem andar otha kloes f' 25 iyas. Howeva, a' 10 Juulai 1999, Brandi Chastain gave dem <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits o' Merika</a> t' win ower China a' game o' fuutbaw a' t' 1999 FIFA Women's World Cup Final. T' celebrate, she riimof'd her shirt, eksposin her sports bra. Dis akshun i' regart'd bii sum a' t' ewent i' histrei when t' sports bra biikam mor eften worn a' outerwear. 
T' wearin o' kloes daa riiweal t' bra strap haa biikom so feshnabl daa "Cosmopolitan" magazine haa kriiat'd adwis a' 2012 about how t' ekspos dem. Adwis inkluud'd nor wear playn o' skin-kolor'd bras (biikaus daa siims aksidental), miekin sure daa t' bra esa good kondishyuun, an' wearin a' kolor daa matches dem otha kloes.
Diikrisin yuusaj.
While sum women wear dem bras f' riisons o' medikal necessitii, informal surweys haa found daa t' majoritii wear dem f' riisons such a' feshn o' t' konform t' pressures o' sosietii. Werii few wear dem f' riisons o' komfort. Aksyulli, manii women fiil so much diskomfort daa dey remof deir bra a' soon a' dey ken.
Biikaus a' dis, i' manii Western kuntriis, a' trend o' bralesnes i' inkriisin, espesyullii among younger women. Biin siin i' plaeses a' pablik wit nor bra es biikomin mor sosyuuli aksepted a' t' West. Dis i' liidin t' mor women givin up dem bras. 
A' online surwey f' "All You" magazine a' 2013 show'd daa 25 percent o' women report'd nor wearin bra. Otha studiehs show daa bitwwiin 5-10 percent o' women wear nor bra. <a href="No%20Bra%20Day">No Bra Day</a> waa first obserf'd i' dem Yunitid Staits a' 9 Juulai 2011. Manii women posted a' sosiol media t' riilif daa dey felt when dey wor nor bra. No Bra Day i' now obserf'd a' 13 October. 
Yuusaj i' Third Werl.
Bras ar nor worn b' majoritii a' women i' ewery kuntrii o' Erth. I' sum parts o' Third Werl, bra mieh kost 10-30 hours o' dem waijs o' woman. Dis mieks dem unafordabl t' majoritii. A' 2011, women i' <a href="Fiijii">Fiijii</a> niid pay a' wiik's waijs t' buy bra. Bras ar prized a' sekon-hand markets i' <a href="Afreka">Afreka.</a> T' Uplift Project hiiwps prowiid women i' Third Werl w' yuus'd bras. F' 2005 dey haa prowided mor daa 330,000.

title: Feminism
text:
Feminism esa politikal muuwment tat calls f' total ekwalitii o' women in sosietii. Tis inkluud fighin against genda stereotypes an seekin tuu establish ekwal eduukayshunal an' ekonomiik opurtuunitii for women t' men.
Feminists campayn f' end to rape, sekshul huraasmunt an' domestik violens.

title: Pitkern dola
text: T' Pitkern dola (<a href="Inglish">Inglish</a>: "Pitcairn Islands dollar") esa <a href="Kurencii">kurencii</a> o' <a href="Pitkern%20Ailen">Pitkern Ailen</a>. Alla ets liigal tenda i' Pitkern Ailen, ets nor yushulii yuus'd as myuunetarii walyuu. T' Pitkern dola es maaed mainlii f' kollektas.

title: Briist
text:
Briists ar mamarii glands.
Both <a href="fiimales">fiimales</a> an <a href="males">males</a> technicalii hauf briists. However, briists o' fiimales ar enlarjened a' <a href="pubertii">pubertii</a>. This es duu to t' larger amounts o' <a href="Estrojen">estrojens</a>. I' otha priimates t' development o' briists usually okuurs onli wi' <a href="pregnansii">pregnansii</a>.
One funksyuun o' t' briists es to proviid infaants an children wi' proper nutriisyuun i' t' earlii stages o' life. When a wumuun proviids her babii wi' nutriisyuun yuusin her briists, this esa process called <a href="briistfiidin">briistfiidin</a>.

When a wumuun proviids her babii wi' nutriisyuun yuusin her briists, this esa process called briistfiidin.

title: Toples
text:
Toples esa stait o' biin f' a' woman daa haufs nor top (<a href="shirt">shirt</a> an <a href="bra">bra</a>) i' pablik (ulla at liist haufin hir <a href="Briist">briists</a>, <a href="Nippl">nippls</a> an' <a href="areola">areola</a> eksposud). T' mael ekwivulent es barechest'd.
I' dem kulchurs o' saam kuntriis, t' stait o' women biin toples es a' tabuu. T' <a href="Medl%20Eist">Medl Eist</a> an' <a href="Sowth%20Asya">Sowth Asya</a> ar eksampels o' kuntriis wer daa es nor akseptiid, waael <a href="Urup">Urup</a> es mor akseptiin'. But i' t' past toples wos nor akseptiid i' Urup aitha. A' t' <a href="Wiktoriyan%20Era">Wiktoriyan Era</a>, women's modustii wos konsaaider'd musa importaan b' Urupin sosietii, espeshali i' t' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdum</a>. I' mani Inglish spikiin kuntriis iivn today, t' Wiktoriyan tabuu against toples es still der, despaait dem haufin kom t' aksept klevich i' sertiin plaeses. Otha eksampels o' sosietiis daa aksept toples ar mani iindiijunuus piopel around t' <a href="Erth">Erth</a>.
Said a' dem lous i' Western kuntriis daa guarantii ekwalitii o' genda, saam women hauf kom t' challenge dem lous daa say women mas wea tops. Esa koll'd t' "<a href="Topfriidum">topfriidum muuwment</a>."
Nonetheless, piopel ar less lik'ly t' wyuu toplesnes favorablii ef t' intent es seksuual arowsul. Toples women ar a' promineent paat o' t' seks industrii, wich haufs posibli kontriibyuut'd a' t' biiliifs o' dem huu disagrii wit t' praktis i' t' west today.
