title: Koukeisiis
text:
Koukeisiis ulla Koukeisiya esa an airea sityuuaitiid b'twiin t' <a href="Blek%20Sii">Blek Sii</a> an <a href="Kaspiyan%20Sii">Kaspiyan Sii</a> an' okkyuupai'd <a href="Rusha">Rusha</a>, <a href="Jorja">Jorja</a>, <a href="Eserbeyjan">Eserbeyjan</a> an <a href="Aarmanya">Aarmanya</a>. Politikli splitt'd intuu <a href="North%20Koukeisiis">North Koukeisiis</a> (Rusha) an <a href="Transkoukeisya">Transkoukeisya</a> (Jorja, Eserbeyjan, Aarmanya).
T' rijion es form'd b' <a href="Koukeisiis%20Mauntens">Koukeisiis Mauntens</a>, an t' biges point o' Urup (<a href="Maun%20Elbrus">Maun Elbrus</a>) es sityuuat'd der.
Histreikli Koukeisiis es a' nachural border bitwiin <a href="Eist%20Urup">Eist Urup</a> an <a href="West%20Asya">West Asya</a>.
linked_text: Koukeisiis ulla Koukeisiya esa an airea sityuuaitiid b'twiin t' Blek Sii an Kaspiyan Sii an' okkyuupai'd [[Rusha]], [[Jorja]], [[Eserbeyjan]] an [[Aarmanya]]. Politikli splitt'd intuu North Koukeisiis (Rusha) an Transkoukeisya (Jorja, Eserbeyjan, Aarmanya). T' rijion es form'd b' Koukeisiis Mauntens, an t' biges point o' Urup (Maun Elbrus) es sityuuat'd der. Histreikli Koukeisiis es a' nachural border bitwiin Eist Urup an [[West Asya]].

title: Vladimir Lenin
text: Vladimir Iliich Lenin (<a href="Rushan">Rushan</a>: "Владимир Ильич Ленин"; <a href="Ieprel%2022">Ieprel 22</a>, <a href="1870">1870</a> — <a href="Jaenyuweri%2021">Jaenyuweri 21</a>, <a href="1924">1924</a>) bin wos wun <a href="Rusha">Rushan</a> revolyuushanar, politishun an teorist. Hii es bin a' maekaa o' t' fas sosialistik kuntrii i' t' Woral (<a href="YoSSR">YoSSR</a>) an t' fas liida o' et.

title: Hachikuu
text:
Hachikuu (<a href="Japaniis">Japaniis</a>: ハチ公) esa <a href="akitainuu">akitainuu</a> <a href="dorg">dorg</a> bin remembren f' his loyalitii tuu his ownaa, <a href="Hidesaburo%20Ueno">Hidesaburo Ueno</a> (<a href="Japaniis">Japaniis</a>: 上野 英三郎), f' huum hi kontinyuud t' weit f' ower 9 iyas aafta Ueno's deth.
Laaef.
Hachikuu s' born orn Novemba 10, 1923, orn a faam neya t' citii a' <a href="Odate">Odate</a>. I' 1924, Hidesaburo Ueno adopt'd him. Hachikuu weit'd his ownaa aafta werk at <a href="Shibuya%20Steyshun">Shibuya Steyshun</a> everi dieh an kontinyuud t' weit aafta Ueno's deth orn Mieh 21, 1925. From daa aantil his deth orn Maach 1935, Hachikuu ritern'd t' Shibuya Steyshun everi dieh t' aweit Ueno's ritern.

title: Svetlana Loboda
text:
Svetlana Sergiyivna Loboda (<a href="Yukrayniian">Yukrayniian</a>: Світла́на Сергі́ївна Лобода́; <a href="Rushan">Rushan</a>: Светлана Сергеевна Лобода) (Oktoeba 18, 1982, <a href="Kiev">Kiev</a>, <a href="YoSSR">YoSSR</a>) esa wun <a href="Yukrayiniian">Yukrayiniian</a> an <a href="Rusha">Rushan</a> singaa. Shii reprisent'd Yukrayn a' <a href="2009%20Uruvishen%20Song%20Kontest">2009 Uruvishen Song Kontest</a> an finish'd wit 12th plaes.
Biografii.
Svetlana Loboda wos barn i' 1982 iya i' t' faemilii o' Sergiy Vasilievich an Natalya Vasilievna. Shii staadied t' <a href="piano">piano</a>, <a href="kondakten">kondakten</a> an <a href="vokal">vokal</a>, shouud tendens f' myuusik an akten. Loboda finish'd myuusik skuul an bekaem t' membaa o' band a' "Cappucino". I' 2003 iya shii hauf'd t' liidin roel i' profeshunal myuusikl "The Equator". Aftaa, at t' end o' t' iya Svetlana kriet'd a nyuu band — "Catch".

title: Fletcha Kristen
text:
Fletcha Kristen (25 Septemba 1764 – 20 September 1793) wos masta's mate a' t' HMS Baunti a' Lieutenant William Bligh's woyej t' <a href="Tahitii">Tahiti</a> biitwiin1787–1789 f' uru. I' t' <a href="Myuutenias%20o%27%20HMS%20Baunti">myuutinii a' t' "Baunti"</a>, Kristen siis'd komand a' t' shep f' Bligh a' 28 April 1789.
Kristen wos born a' 25 Septemba 1764, a' hiis familii hoem a' Moorland Close, Eaglesfield, klos t' Cockermouth i' Cumberland, Ingland. Fletcha's faada's par a' t' familii hauf'd come f' <a href="Ailen%20o%27%20Maan">t' Ailen o' Maan</a> an' mos a' hiis great-faad wos dem histreik Deemster, dems orijinel familii las name McCrystyn.
Fletcha wos t' broda a' Edward an' Humphrey, b'in t' trii sullun a' Charles Kristen a' Moorland Close an' a' t' larj Ewanrigg Hall propatei i' Dearham, Cumberland, a atornii i' law wit' Manx jentrii, an' hiis maia Ann Dikson.

title: Raelian Muuwment
text:
T' Raelian Muuwment esa <a href="Nyuu%20rilijuus%20muuwment">Nyuu rilijuus muuwment</a>. Ets konsaaider'd t' bii a <a href="UFO%20riligin">UFO riligin</a> basiid a' t' biliif i' extraterrestrials. T' Muuwment was founded b' <a href="Claude%20Vorilhon">Claude Vorilhon</a> i' dem 1970s. 
T' Raelian Muuwment tiiches daa t' <a href="Hyuuman">Hyuuman species</a> was criiated b' a' race o' extraterrestrial daa dem call "Elohim". Dem Raelians hauf a' atheistic riligin, but dem biliive daa t' Elohim hauf biin mistaken t' bii <a href="God">gods</a> i' deir own raait. title: Corazón valiente
text:
Corazón valiente ("Fearless Heart)" esa <a href="Spanish">Spanish-laenghwij</a> <a href="telenovela">telenovela</a> prodyuus'd bii t' <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits</a>-beis'd <a href="televisiien">televisiien</a> network <a href="Telemundo">Telemundo</a>, featuring a' ensembl cast. <a href="Adriana%20Fonseca">Adriana Fonseca</a>, <a href="Ximena%20Duque">Ximena Duque</a>, <a href="Jos%C3%A9%20Luis%20Res%C3%A9ndez">José Luis Reséndez</a> an <a href="Fabi%C3%A1n%20R%C3%ADos">Fabián Ríos</a> starred as dem mien protaagonists. <a href="Ayl%C3%ADn%20M%C3%BAjica">Aylín Mújica</a> an Manuel Landeta starred as dem mien antaagonists.
Telemundo aired "Corazón valiente" wiiknights at 9pm/8c from March 6, 2012 to Januarii 7, 2013 riplaciin "<a href="Flor%20salvaje">Flor salvaje</a>". On Januarii 8, 2013 "<a href="La%20patrona">La patrona</a>" ripleis'd "Corazón valiente." As wit most o' dem otha novelas, Telemundo broadcast closed kapsyuuns i' Inglish, as well as Spanish.
Plot.
This esa t' storii o' t' friendship bitwiin tuu girls i' a' riimot citii calla Villa de Bravo. Ángela Valdez (Sofía Sanabria), humble an swiit, waa t' daughter o' Miguel Valdez (<a href="Jorge%20Luis%20Pila">Jorge Luis Pila</a>) t' bodiiguard o' t' powerful an wealthii Sandoval Navarro familii. Samantha Sandoval Navarro was t' rich girl guarded bii Miguel Valdéz. Dem tuu girls' lives ar foreva chaynged when Samantha i' kidnapped, resulting i' Miguel Valdéz sacrificing his life t' save her. Efta what happened, dem girls were separated.
Ángela and Samantha miit again afta eightiin years. Ángela (<a href="Adriana%20Fonseca">Adriana Fonseca</a>) i' mariid t' Luis Martínez (<a href="Gabriel%20Valenzuela">Gabriel Valenzuela</a>) haa a' daughter Violeta (Nicole Arci) an works as a' baker. For her part, Samantha (<a href="Ximena%20Duque">Ximena Duque</a>), works as a bodiiguard. Samantha thiinks o' t' idea o' inviting Ángela to work wi' her; Ángela aksepts an assigns her t' misyun t' protect Génesis Arroyo, t' daughter o' a' multimillionaire lawyer neim'd Juan Marcos Arroyo (<a href="Jos%C3%A9%20Luis%20Res%C3%A9ndez">José Luis Reséndez</a>) who is unfortunatlii mariid to Isabel Uriarte (<a href="Sonia%20Smith">Sonia Smith</a>) a' proud an evil woman who i' unfaithful ivin wi' his ouun bodiiguard. Meanwhile, Samantha i' ordered t' protect Willy del Castillo (<a href="Fabi%C3%A1n%20R%C3%ADos">Fabián Ríos</a>) her first love, who has become a whimsical playboy an womanizer. Samantha decides not t' reveal anything o' her past, but hi ends up discovering who she is an love arises between them.
Thus, Ángela and Samantha will hauf t' fight wi' all dem obstacles daa their enemies will put them through i' order t' b' hapii wi' t' piopel dey love, while always having a' brave heart.

title: Newsmax TV
text:
Newsmax TV i' konserwatif nyuus channel i' dem <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits o' Merika</a> own'd bii Newsmax Media. T' channel primarilii broadkasts f' et's Nyuu York bas'd studio an' haa et's headquarters in West Palm Biich, Florida. Et haa a nyuus tawk format day an' night w' dokyuumentariis a' wiikents.
T' channel waa kriiat'd bii Merikan juurnalist an' Newsmax CEO Christopher Ruddy. Et laanch'd a' Jyuun 16, 2014 t' 35 million TV subskribers thruu DirecTV an' Dish Network. A' Mieh 2019 t' netwurk riiches around 75 million homes i' dem Yunited Staits o' Merika.
Newsmax haa far-right politikal stans, fiichurin mani right-wing nyuus an' tawk personalitiis. T' kompanii haa hir'd mani former Fox News personalitiis. Dem inkluud Greg Kelly, Rob Schmitt an' Bob Sellers. "The Washington Post" haa deskrib'd t' netwurk a' "landin spot f' kabl nyuus personalitiis i' niid a' nyuu home". Dis i' biikaus a' mani personalitiis comin here efta leafin otha networks f' kontrowerserii.

title: Minecraft
text:
Minecraft (Mienkraaft) esa <a href="Swiiden">Swiidish</a> sandboks <a href="video%20geiim">video geiim</a> mied b' <a href="Mojang%20Studios">Mojang Studios</a> i' 2009. Et waas rileasd i' 2011. Playyes ken bild virtually anythin. Samtaims, et ken be a servivel geiim as well as a' sandboks. Mojang, t' meikas o' Minecraft, ar hedkwortd i' <a href="Stockholm">Stockholm</a>, <a href="Swiiden">Swiiden</a>.
Histrei.
Minecraft waas meid b' <a href="Markus%20Persson">Markus 'Notch' Persen</a> and <a href="Jens%20Bergsten">Yens 'Jeb' Bergsten</a> i' Stockholm. T' beta waas released i' <a href="Swiidish">Swiidish</a> an <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a> i' Mieh, 2009. T' geiim waas ofisholi released on Nowemba 18, 2011. Notch sold t' geiim to <a href="Microsoft">Microsoft</a> on Septemba 14, 2014 f' $2.5 billion. Jeb es nau t' liida. T geiim haufs mani updates. Et es t' mas played geiim on t' Erth as o' 2021. Minecraft haufs nor a <a href="Norfuk">Norfuk</a> laenghwij opshun, but et haufs sam kuntriis' <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a> dialects: <a href="Ostrielya">Ostrielya</a>, <a href="Nyuu%20Ziilan">Nyuu Ziilan</a>, <a href="Sowth%20Afreka">Sowth Afreka</a>, <a href="Kaneda">Kaneda</a>, t' <a href="Yunitid%20Staits%20o%27%20Merika">Yunitid Staits</a> an t' <a href="Yunitid%20Kingdum">Yunitid Kingdum</a>.
Minecon.
<a href="Minecon">Minecon</a> es a' ewent held evr'ii iya b' <a href="Mojang">Mojang</a>. Meni salan getha to faind out 'bout t' next updeit. T' firs wan waas held i' 2010, i' [Washington DC|[Woshingten D.C]]. Et has been held i' <a href="Paris">Paris</a>, <a href="Nyuu%20York">Nyuu York</a>, <a href="Los%20Angeles">Los Angeles</a>, <a href="Seattle">Seattle</a>, <a href="Orlando">Orlando</a> an <a href="Salem">Salem</a> bifo, but nor i' t' <a href="Southern%20Hemisphere">Southern Hemisphere</a> yet. I' 2017, et waas reneimd t' Minecon Erth. I' 2019, et waas reneimd t' Minecon Liew. I' 2020, et waas reneimd t' Minecraft Liew. Due to t' <a href="COVID-19%20pandemic">COVID-19 pandemic</a>, Minecraft Liew 2020 waas held wit noe salan deya, i' Stockholm. Et was orijinli goen t' bii i' Orlando f' a' sekan tiem as Minecraft Festewaal, det has biin postpoend t' 2022.

Et es t' mas played geiim on t' Erth as o' 2021. title: Awarua
text: Awarua ("tuu haabas" iin <a href="Dem%20Kuuk%20Ailen%20Maaori">Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori</a>) es t' kapitel o' <a href="Dem%20Kuuk%20Ailen">Dem Kuuk Ailen</a>. It es orn t' ailen o' <a href="Rarotonga">Rarotonga</a>. 4,906 o' dem salan liew i' t' Awarua Distrikt.
linked_text: Awarua ("tuu haabas" iin [[Dem Kuuk Ailen Maaori]]) es t' kapitel o' [[Dem Kuuk Ailen]]. It es orn t' ailen o' Rarotonga. 4,906 o' dem salan liew i' t' Awarua Distrikt.

title: Mani
text: Mani es eni item or werifaibl rekord det es jenrilii eksept'd es a <a href="peiment">peiment</a> f' guuds an serwises (e.g f' <a href="wetls">wetls</a>) an repliesment o' dets, sach as tekses, iin a kuntrii or soshio-ekonomik kontekst.
linked_text: Mani es eni item or werifaibl rekord det es jenrilii eksept'd es a peiment f' guuds an serwises (e.g f' [[wetls]]) an repliesment o' dets, sach as tekses, iin a kuntrii or soshio-ekonomik kontekst.

title: Wetls
text: Wetls es a substens det ken bi iiten bai salan an/or kriichas, f' nyuutrients. Wetls es jenrilii o' kriicha, plant or fungal orijin.
linked_text: Wetls es a substens det [[ken]] bi iiten bai salan an/or kriichas, f' nyuutrients. Wetls es jenrilii o' kriicha, plant or fungal orijin.

title: LSBT
text: LSBT ("LGBT") es an ekronim det stands f' Lesbien, Suuta, Baiseksh'l an Trensjendaa ("Lesbian, Gay, Bisexual and Transgender"). Iin <a href="Norfuk">Norfuk</a>/<a href="Pitkern">Pitkern</a>, t' uni letaa difr'nt iin t' <a href="Inglish">Inglish</a> ekronim es t' "S" as t' "G" (as t' Norfuk/Pitkern werd f' "gay" es "suuta").
linked_text: LSBT ("LGBT") es an ekronim det stands f' Lesbien, Suuta, Baiseksh'l an Trensjendaa ("Lesbian, Gay, Bisexual and Transgender"). Iin [[Norfuk]]/[[Pitkern]], t' uni letaa difr'nt iin t' [[Inglish]] ekronim es t' "S" as t' "G" (as t' Norfuk/Pitkern werd f' "gay" es "suuta").

title: Palestiin
text: Palestiin esa kuntrii iin t' <a href="Med%27l%20Eist">Med'l Eist</a>. Deya es kurentlii a konflikt bitwiin <a href="Esrail">Esrail</a> an Palestiin, inkluudin t' konflikt owaa t' sitii o' <a href="Jerusalem">Jerusalem</a>.
linked_text: Palestiin esa kuntrii iin t' Med'l Eist. Deya es kurentlii a konflikt bitwiin [[Esrail]] an Palestiin, inkluudin t' konflikt owaa t' sitii o' Jerusalem.

title: Port Morsbii
text: Port Morsbii es t' kepitel o' <a href="Papua%20Nyuu%20Gini">Papua Nyuu Gini</a>.
linked_text: Port Morsbii es t' kepitel o' [[Papua Nyuu Gini]].

title: Lae
text: Lae es t' sekan biges sitii iin <a href="Papua%20Nyuu%20Gini">Papua Nyuu Gini</a>.
linked_text: Lae es t' sekan biges sitii iin [[Papua Nyuu Gini]].

title: Klorth
text: Klorth ar eni item worn orn t' badii. Taipikli, klorth s' mied f' <a href="fabriks">fabriks</a> ala <a href="tekstail">tekstail</a>.
linked_text: Klorth ar eni item worn orn t' badii. Taipikli, klorth s' mied f' fabriks ala tekstail.
